translate English day6_cr_rkn_f29662cd:


    nar "The moment I say it, my throat shakes.{w} Claire doesn't seem to notice; she throws her arms around my neck and embraces me."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_e0b67045:


    nar "In front of me, the snow-white cloth flutters and sways like a mirage."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_9cde41c8:


    cr "I'm so happy!{w} Really, really happy!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_da297b25:


    nar "I'd certainly like to turn around and say \"About what?\"{w} But I can't bully her like that.{w} I relax and see her smiling."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_bf863d7c:


    nar "Her smile is so bright it instantly evaporates any regrets I may have had."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_e111c841:


    nar "Even if this choice is the wrong one, right now her joy makes me happier than anything else.{w} So I smile back at her."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b22cc340:


    nar "The feelings I feel in this moment are my answer to her."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_a6e00b3e:


    cr "Lord [na], I do have more to tell you.{w} It's embarrassing, however."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_5cd3d74e:


    pl "More embarrassing than confessing to me?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_48583df3:


    cr "It's much like that, actually.{w} About that, well..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_5156dfb7:


    cr "I suppose the blood had rushed to my head, so I didn't have time to be embarrassed about anything..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_bf1005bd:


    cr "But anyway, now that I'm calm, I'm incredibly embarrassed!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_3a415e21:


    pl "Okay, okay.{w} Anyway, what's up?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_9d34deb1:


    cr "W-Well, the thing is..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_bc7e59ee:


    cr "Here I am, wearing myself out to profess my true feelings and knowing they line up with yours."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_8b98a6ec:


    cr "But this dress I wore all the way here has gotten dirty, and the man who embraced me smells like death and decay...{w} And your family and finances are both utterly normal..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_88f52a7d:


    pl "Hey, this is turning out to be more embarrassing for me than you..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_f71cc9ce:


    cr "And yet I'm so, so genuinely happy right now."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_afb8be39:


    cr "I feel so much more satisfied now than going to see a wonderful movie or receiving a gemstone as a gift."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_180ca9bb:


    cr "Am I simply being foolish and misunderstanding?{w} I'm aware I lack life experience."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_525a42ed:


    pl "...Even if you are, if you're satisfied, that means this makes you happy, right?{w} I don't have much place to tell you how to feel."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_d2a93e94:


    cr "Hee hee. You're right.{w} But I can't allow myself to be happy alone.{w} How do you feel, Lord [na]?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_22df5a8e:


    pl "Me?{w} Well, I--"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_17083724:


    nar "The sun's white light comes in through the small window.{w} We flinch at the sudden illumination, then turn to look that way."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_815a94a7:


    cr "Look! The sky has cleared while we were talking!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b84bb11e:


    nar "Claire bounds up the stairs, forgetting all about the shoes she left on the floor."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_bbcce26b:


    nar "Her dress hem is filthy, and the soles of her feet are a deep, sooty black.{w} But they go perfectly with her innocent steps."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_57a74519:


    nar "I go up as well and gaze out the window.{w} The white dust that has risen into the sky is glittering."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_48052629:


    nar "Claire's white clothes catch the light too, gleaming in the same way.{w} Thanks to how bright the sun is, her blue hair reminds me even more of the sky back home."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_fafb26e0:


    pl "Feels kinda...{w} I dunno, strange, when it's bright out here."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_ffea723d:


    cr "Do you think so?{w} The white night has been continuing for a good while, so I don't feel like it's all that unusual."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b7c20944:


    pl "Yeah? It's kinda felt gloomy for a while to me.{w} It's, well... It's quiet here. And the air quality's bad."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b26c68d4:


    cr "Yes, but I love it all the same.{w} It's quiet, but cozy.{w} The perfect for having a secret romance!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_9de9b24e:


    cr "Oh, tell me if you knew this already."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_09ceb896:


    cr "This used to be an emergency stairwell, but since most of the priests go through lobby, nobody really uses it anymore."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_7d455afe:


    pl "Sounds like you're underestimating me, missy!{w} I knew all about that from the start."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_10b6f7ac:


    cr "But the two of us gave passion and meaning to this abandoned place."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_eaf3375f:


    cr "And now this woeful place is somewhere very special to us.{w} Isn't that just wonderful?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_8a66e792:


    pl "Giving meaning to some stuff or a place or whatever isn't meaningless.{w} I should have expected such sensitivities from a young lady who doesn't know anything about the world."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_84d9e4b1:


    cr "Ugh! You're so mean!{w} I should have expected such dried-up sensitivities from someone on the cleanup crew."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_c5c21f0c:


    nar "I look down from the small window into the flower gardens.{w} Despite Maya's maintenance, there's still ivy everywhere."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_4ff3fd54:


    nar "I see familiar pink hair drift behind the ivy's gaps.{w} It's about lunchtime, actually, isn't it?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_5808b6f0:


    nar "She's so tiny, squatting among the crazy tall roses.{w} When I look at her from above like this, she looks like she's about to get eaten by plants."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_0b0980c2:


    pl "Ma--"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_3f554248:


    nar "As I open my mouth to call out her name, my vision suddenly tilts.{w} My shoulder hits the floor.{w} Claire looks at me right up close, her face sullen."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_46ec283a:


    pl "Ow...{w} What'd you do that for?! You could have hurt me, Claire!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_61e500ff:


    cr "Oh, well, excuse me.{w} Know that I make it a rule to repay rudeness with rudeness!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_ef2056ce:


    pl "What do you mean by rudeness?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_38d02e30:


    cr "I mean just what I said.{w} Lord [na], the two of us are now clandestine lovers!{w} Do you understand that?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_dd9d1f65:


    pl "I mean, I guess so..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_bf51b4f3:


    cr "And yet you just tried to call someone else over.{w} You're essentially ignoring my feelings!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_f3c5b8b7:


    cr "Not only are you rude, you're also cowardly."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_678b2849:


    pl "Claire... Look, it wasn't on purpose."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_99c51fda:


    cr "The fact that you can do such a thing accidentally is even more concerning, if you ask me."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_d3413beb:


    pl "Urk..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_ccbd21f3:


    cr "And being so gloomy about it won't change anything, you know!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_f887d319:


    pl "Yeah, I get it, I get it! I'll apologize!{w} Anyway, what do you want from me?!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_ed76e1f3:


    cr "I think I'm finally getting through to you. Would you like forgiveness?{w} My desire is really quite simple."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_3bb39f40:


    cr "I want you to make an earnest oath to me. Swear by your heart."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_d9f6d11c:


    pl "An oath?{w} Err... Like, saying \"amen\"?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_a505a2d8:


    cr "Goodness me! I've never seen someone so ignorant!{w} You're like a foreign man from a distant island somewhere. It's just the greatest."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_d48943ea:


    pl "You're teasing me again!{w} Also, I've been wanting to tell you this, but I'm not from an island."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_2dfae87a:


    nar "Claire gives me a playful smile; her tension must have dissolved.{w} The long eyelashes adorning her large eyes are almost close enough to touch my forehead."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_3b24e531:


    nar "I notice myself having an unusual desire for those eyes.{w} She looks at me, surely noticing the unease in my own eyes."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_2d06d350:


    cr "In the capital, when we make an oath, we do it with these."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_0b8c53c4:


    pl "Your eyes?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b1c510c0:


    cr "What? My eyes?{w} No! My lips! LIPS!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_939b8753:


    cr "A kiss to seal an oath, they call it.{w} So that each time you breathe, you think of that person."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_03aa9200:


    cr "And each time you talk it is for that person alone.{w} It's a very meaningful, romantic superstition."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b2bf27e9:


    pl "A superstition?{w} You mean like blowing a flute at night to get snakes to come out?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_bb8b30ad:


    cr "No, if I had to compare it to anything, it would be like the red string of fate.{w} Hmm... Judging by your reaction, you still haven't had your first kiss, Lord [na]."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_d4d1c22e:


    pl "...Are you upset by that?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_5d931d96:


    cr "No, I'm rather fortunate."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_eab77e49:


    nar "\"Because now you, too, will have meaning,\" she says before closing her eyes, cheeks slightly flushed."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_3bb59910:


    nar "I simply watch her approach with bated breath, forgetting to even close my own."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_4114c16b:



    nvl clear
    "\n The clouds in the capital are impatient. As they conceal the sunlight from above, she presses her mouth to mine like a bird wanting food, then squirms her little tongue in through the gap."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_aa0a7373:


    "Even now, I hesitate to close my eyes.{w} I feel like when I open them again, the entire world will have changed into something I don't understand.{w} But her hair is in my eyes, and her face fills my vision, forcing me to close them anyway."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_641990cd:


    et "The sunless world behind my eyelids is very dark. Watery sounds stab into my ears and imprint on my brain. The stone floor at my back makes me think of the bottom of the sea, which I've never seen before."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_5f1a46d9:



    nvl clear
    "\n With my mind on strange things, Claire loops her arms around my neck and continues to earnestly move her tongue.{w} She does so violently, as though starved for the information she usually searches for. It feels like she's expecting it to be hidden inside of my mouth.{w} She runs her tongue across each ill-shapen tooth before pulling it back into her own mouth, her saliva falling all over my gums."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_6b4a9460:


    et "Captured by her aggressive kiss, I decide to stop awkwardly moving my own tongue, and instead relax myself even more, as though sinking into a deep place.{w} I don't think I'd be able to escape her, even though all she has on me is a single tongue between my thin lips."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_cr_rkn_92b18915:


    "\n I keenly feel my head trembling as she breathes heavily and toys with my ear, making me anxious.{w} I think of my kiss with her that night. I'm embarrassed.{w} With a deep darkness eating away at my mind, she climbs on top of me, slowly pushing me down under her weight. Opening my eyes becomes a scarier and scarier prospect."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_78fc9399:


    et "If I open them now, I'm afraid she'll be smiling the same way she had."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_cr_rkn_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_cr_rkn_d68e1411:


    "\n \"Hahhh!\""


translate English day6_cr_rkn_dd5f68bb:


    et "As soon as her lips finally pull away from their seemingly eternal kiss, the darkness before me departs, and bright light shines back in.{w} The illusion dominating my mind, of being on the ocean floor, vanishes as well.{w} I focus on gasping for breath like a fish that jumped out of the water and experienced the dryness land for the first time."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_742ab85b:



    nvl clear
    "\n Claire breathes just as heavily as she looks down at me, a strong light at her back.{w} She has such fair skin, and it makes her tongue look all the redder. Come to think of it, I've never gotten a good look at it like this before.{w} For some reason, I shudder when I think of it having been inside my mouth."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_4d1b104c:


    et "Probably not realizing how I'm feeling, a smile soon comes to her face flushed crimson.{w} But that smile isn't like the one that night.{w} This is different; it's one I've never seen before. A typical smile to hide her embarrassment.{w} That's not an expression you can make without knowledge of the situation."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b8e07a8e:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I love you, Lord [na]...\""


translate English day6_cr_rkn_c6582131:


    "I hear Claire say my name, and that she loves me, but it feels more like a statement of gratitude to me.{w} I turn towards her, as she keeps her face averted from mine, and give the same response, merely moving my lips."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_fcd6c255:


    et "The cold warmth makes me immensely, incredibly sad."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_cr_rkn_ae07b9f0:


    nar "I use a cloth to wipe up the miserable scene that spilled out of us."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_341407ac:


    nar "I'd wanted to get rid of these clothes anyway.{w} And now I guess I have to."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_11d9de19:


    nar "Claire, who has picked up her own clothes and put them back on, smiles at me.{w} What does she find so funny, wearing such filthy things?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_84ba314c:


    cr "Umm, Lord [na]...{w} I'm fully aware of my rudeness, but was that truly your first kiss?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_9fb5179a:


    pl "I already told you it was, remember?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_94e2ab30:


    cr "Ahh... Thank goodness.{w} You truly are amazing, Lord [na]!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_0ccb84c3:


    pl "What, for always bringing a handkerchief around?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_ea489bdc:


    cr "That too, but what I especially mean to compliment is your technique."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_e1fee6be:


    pl "My... what?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b80551fe:


    cr "I was pretty sure the other Cleanup Department priests would never leave someone as standout as you alone..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_818ca8ad:


    cr "But now I'm sure of it.{w} You've already experienced this with another girl."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_0218ac68:


    pl "Huh?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_15a32910:


    cr "I was quite happy you gave me your lips, but for someone like you to engage in this ritualistic destruction of virginity?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_4c75dcef:


    cr "it must have been quite boring for you..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_7c946069:


    nar "I want to deny it, but I soon realize I can't.{w} I'd forgotten about my first experience until just now."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_5dc0b1db:


    pl "Oh, don't dig your own grave here...{w} It might not have been my first time with this sort of thing, but,"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_c66913c9:


    pl "Well... I do intend to take responsibility for you."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_171ff4c1:


    cr "Ah, how wonderful!{w} I had no idea a girl in love viewed the world through such rose-tinted lenses!{w} I've fallen for you all over again."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_716d72d5:


    pl "Okay, okay..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_7e8858b2:


    nar "She's imagining something I didn't intend for--again--but I don't have the strength left to point that out."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_0d89e531:


    nar "My head is swimming with relief at having overcome this situation and worry at what will happen in the future."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_28613cb1:


    pl "Your clothes got dirty. Will you be okay?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_05e0709f:


    cr "It's alright. I came prepared for at least this much.{w} They actually didn't get as dirty as I expected them to."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_98d8766c:


    pl "...Don't wear stuff like that from now on."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_9498506d:


    cr "Too stimulating for you?{w} No need to worry. I won't be wearing this again."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_51c1ffe7:


    cr "These are the clothes I brought to this fight--in which I emerged victorious!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_2b0ec795:


    nar "Claire grabs onto my arm, her expression innocent.{w} I feel spineless for letting this little girl toy with me so much."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_f2340e88:


    pl "I went through all that work to untangle your hair for you, but now it's a mess again.{w} It must be hard to maintain when it's that long."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_4610770e:


    cr "It's okay. I'm in a really, fantastically good mood!{w} This must be the happiness of being with the one you love!"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_af5cc5db:


    pl "Hey, Claire... About the question I couldn't answer before..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_aac044e5:


    cr "Yes?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_28222a33:


    pl "...If you're happy, then I'm happy too."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_62362fb3:


    cr "Eeee!{w} Lord [na], look at you, sounding so gallant. Ehehe..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_ab31d5e3:


    nar "After seeing Claire off, I sit on the stairs for a while."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_4c128c18:


    nar "She kept calling me cool, or amazing, or whatever.{w} But that's a terrible misunderstanding."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_0b405615:



    nar "I've never even held hands with a woman before.{w} I'm sure she was thinking about how terrible I am."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_3bee35d1:


    nar "Maybe she was acting lighthearted to conceal her losing hope in me.{w} Maybe she was comparing me to her fiancé."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_9f993027:


    nar "Or maybe even to another man entirely..."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b0a9f8ae:


    nar "I walk out, staggering under my own weight."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_1885f789:


    nar "Mentally, I'm exhausted, and yet my body feels as light as a feather."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_b8a4a636:


    nar "My legs move on their own, as if they don't belong to me, wandering this way and that in the temple.{w} My surroundings keep changing, and quite a few people pass by me."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_57c893cf:


    nar "What have I done? What's going to happen now?"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_54f068c4:


    nar "If word of what I've done gets out, everyone at the temple will start giving me second looks."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_669bb0bf:


    nar "......"


translate English day6_cr_rkn_89dca27b:



    nvl clear
    "\n When I raise my head, I see a light. A brilliantly bright light that urges me forward, the type that burns forever, unable to be extinguished. It welcomes me."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_761c75b8:


    "I haven't simply been wandering. I returned to this place."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_e99f4a4d:


    et "Two big wings, so white they're almost blinding, clearly not of this world."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_9271b365:



    nvl clear
    "\n My vision darkens, my eyes unable to bear the light in all its brilliance. My head naturally falls forward, and I drop to my knees."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_6b214259:


    "I raise my trembling hands, reaching out to touch her skin.{w} But I don't know how to do it properly. I'm utterly deplorable."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_2f667f8b:


    "Still, the angel gives even a lowlife like me a chance. I'm able to touch her. Tears fall from my eyes unintentionally."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_8e94b736:


    et "I grasp her soft hands in mine and weep like a newborn baby."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_af63e1de:



    nvl clear
    "\n But I can't confess to my sin.{w} After all, that sin doesn't belong only to me, but to Claire as well.{w} All I can do is cry onto the angel made manifest--and ruminate on my sin."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_cd90e1b4:


    "I've violated Clione in a way that I can't take responsibility for.{w} I promised to help her, but didn't try and correct her even though I knew she was wrong.{w} I've forced her life even further off the proper path."


translate English day6_cr_rkn_731e6970:


    "Under that spilling, radiant light, the only thing that remains is me, in all my insolence."


