    nvl clear


translate English day7_cr_8804abba:



    nvl clear
    "\n I had a very, very long dream. With my vision blurred and my head throbbing in pain as if trapped in a vice, it feels like I've been asleep for seven days."


translate English day7_cr_c633cf33:


    "All I know for sure is that my consciousness remains enthralled in that otherworldly dream, though I can't for the life of me remember what occured."


translate English day7_cr_9b7f7973:


    "I feel as though it was a scary dream, but also a good dream."


translate English day7_cr_94aca8d8:


    "With long dreams, they're usually so enjoyable that you never want to wake up--or so horrific that it's impossible to come back to reality."


translate English day7_cr_648c3dd7:


    "I don't think any more deeply about it though. So instead, I bury my pounding head in my pillow again.{w} I'm sick of my own thoughts."


translate English day7_cr_d7ae7cd2:


    "How much time have I wasted thinking about this stupid dream? Countless hours for sure."


translate English day7_cr_c4056ed6:


    et "But I don't need to anymore.{w} Because the angel now speaks to me in reality, not just in my dreams..."


translate English day7_cr_478b31fc:



    nvl clear
    "\n I slightly lift my head off the bed, then look out the window at the pure white light shining into my room."


translate English day7_cr_8105756b:


    "The sun, having set during the night, now rises again to welcome the morning.{w} Even the simple sight of the scenery outside the window makes me naturally think it's morning now."


translate English day7_cr_91031fe1:


    "My body feels heavy.{w} I squeeze my eyes shut, but the pounding in my head doesn't stop. I doubt I'll be able to rest any longer."


translate English day7_cr_9cc593e7:


    "Maybe it isn't just me--maybe I really did sleep for seven days. The thought actually excited me for a moment, but I know it's obviously not true."


translate English day7_cr_04282fa1:


    et "As my mind continues to awaken from the dream, my memories of yesterday come rushing back. It's time to go over all the things I need to do today."


translate English day7_cr_06a49c8f:



    nvl clear
    "\n First I need to get out of bed.{w} I should grab a wash stand before the community space is flooded with people and get ready for the morning.{w} I should probably also wash the clothes that have piled up."


translate English day7_cr_eebace9d:


    et "Once I'm all set for the day and looking fresh, I'll say hello to Maya, and then I need to take the bishop's class.{w} I'm a little uncomfortable at the thought of seeing her, but I just need to listen--no problem there."


translate English day7_cr_f0780563:



    nvl clear
    "\n My work is rough, but I think I can manage it.{w} I'm still a newcomer here, but I've started to grow accustomed to things."


translate English day7_cr_b456ec53:


    "But right now, under this familiar ceiling, I'm covered in a blanket that smells like sour skin.{w} From outside the door, I can hear the usual sounds of priests getting ready for the day."


translate English day7_cr_33fa2f05:


    "I could do it, but...I don't want to.{w} That's includes my Cleanup Department work and everything else--like getting out of bed."


translate English day7_cr_58c1b5f6:


    et "Is it a mere folly or is it laziness?{w} Whichever it is, I rest my hands back on my stomach and try to fall asleep again."


translate English day7_cr_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_cr_f614fe7f:


    et "\n \"Words have a lot of weight to them, don't they?\""


translate English day7_cr_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_cr_7be71fc5:



    nvl clear
    "\n I lie there for about ten minutes, I think."


translate English day7_cr_c96b4327:


    et "What finally gets my heavy body up again is not the unease at things falling quiet outside my room, but because I know that's just what I'm supposed to do."


translate English day7_cr_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_cr_52451a50:


    nar "A damp wind blows past my eyes, which are rough and dry at the moment.{w} I look again to see the sky is awfully cloudy."


translate English day7_cr_a2a27202:


    nar "Before entering the room, I stop myself for a moment.{w} About ten people come out of the room at once; roll call must be over."


translate English day7_cr_ba471c17:


    my "[na2]?"


translate English day7_cr_dc7470cb:


    nar "I look towards the familiar voice."


translate English day7_cr_55977acf:


    nar "The other priests look towards us, stretching their legs a bit, then disperse down whatever hallway they need to go down."


translate English day7_cr_1a4aba79:


    pl "Maya! Good morning."


translate English day7_cr_0875c0a4:


    my "Good morning. You're late today...{w} I thought you weren't coming."


translate English day7_cr_e66e66aa:


    pl "Haha!{w} I slept in. I thought I wouldn't be able to see you today, so I'm glad you called out to me."


translate English day7_cr_3c7648c3:


    pl "Are you off to work?"


translate English day7_cr_a140b480:


    my "Mmm... Actually, I was waiting for you. I wanted to say hello..."


translate English day7_cr_e8b473e7:


    pl "Y-You did?"


translate English day7_cr_aacbd590:


    my "N-Not like that. It's just, I was worried about you... from yesterday...{w} Are you feeling well?"


translate English day7_cr_d2bffe7d:


    nar "Yesterday... I certainly saw the angel's light.{w} Despite receiving her blessing, I couldn't tell her of my mistake."


translate English day7_cr_bcba8b6f:


    nar "Likely, in her position, she had questions--or just felt frustrated."


translate English day7_cr_38ce7b08:


    pl "...Eh, I'm fine. Sorry for worrying you like that.{w} Oh, hey! Want to go to work together? I'll help you out."


translate English day7_cr_1f132139:


    my "No... I just wanted to make sure you were okay, [na2]."


translate English day7_cr_2ef9ae4d:


    my "I'm a Cleanup Department priest too. I can't always rely on you and Cue.{w} I'll try my best to go it alone today."


translate English day7_cr_5507c6e5:


    pl "Hey, if that's what you want, I support you... But will you really be alright?"


translate English day7_cr_fc479754:


    my "I'm sure whatever I do will be simple anyway, so... I'll be okay."


translate English day7_cr_698a9c63:


    my "I think you should definitely go over your job today, though...{w} Cue had a really dark look on his face..."


translate English day7_cr_d3ddb810:


    pl "Huh... I see.{w} But if there's anything you need from me, don't hesitate to call me. Okay?"


translate English day7_cr_3334fc23:


    my "......"


translate English day7_cr_6e83e19d:


    pl "Maya...?"


translate English day7_cr_bf80cc45:


    my "If anything's bothering you, you can tell me too, okay?"


translate English day7_cr_052c7040:


    my "I might not be able to help much, but...{w} Promise me you'll do that."


translate English day7_cr_d1ff7c28:


    pl "Oh, uh... Yeah. I will."


translate English day7_cr_0eed99fb:


    nar "Maya walks down the hallway, her little back to me.{w} The marks of an angel are certainly on that back."


translate English day7_cr_c20efc21:


    nar "I know her secret, but I can't reveal my secret to her."


translate English day7_cr_34953a4f:


    nar "Even though angels are supposed to hear my confession and forgive my sins."


translate English day7_cr_faee0fa8:


    nar "But I didn't confess, so she hasn't carried out her own role either."


translate English day7_cr_8db4635a:


    nar "That's probably what Maya is worried about, and why she tried to get a true promise from me.{w} Just like Claire, who wanted that kind of surety from me."


translate English day7_cr_c9a6d952:


    nar "But I've already made an oath to her. Which means all I can do is keep lying to this angel.{w} All to protect Claire."


translate English day7_cr_79f83939:


    nar "I wonder if Maya is mad about it.{w} Maybe she's scared of others learning her secret."


translate English day7_cr_33da2e68:


    nar "Or maybe she now has another secret--one I don't know about."


translate English day7_cr_e7e93915:


    pl "What do you think about it?"


translate English day7_cr_53c83867:


    nar "I borrow her name and ask the question; the man in front of me answers without turning around."


translate English day7_cr_0920d588:


    sc "I've no interest in talking behind people's backs."


translate English day7_cr_ac3ee91a:


    pl "It's not that... I just want to hear your opinion.{w} You've got some interest in people watching, right?"


translate English day7_cr_646ec1eb:


    sc "Yeah, but only because the two of you never do a good job at work."


translate English day7_cr_30c12f08:


    nar "He proceeds down the woodland path without stopping.{w} The soil and the air, still thick with the moisture of previous rains, calm me down for some reason."


translate English day7_cr_b15d4c21:


    nar "The cloudy sky is dark, and the dense tree cover makes it hard to see much.{w} If I lose focus, I'm liable to lose my way."


translate English day7_cr_535d8450:


    nar "To prevent that, I keep my eyes on that silver hair in front of me as I go."


translate English day7_cr_a87626bd:


    sc "She's... Maya is definitely hiding something.{w} Though I don't believe things will go as expected."


translate English day7_cr_b671b9c7:


    pl "Any idea what that something is?"


translate English day7_cr_fd0c3817:


    sc "I've never thought about it. Didn't seem like the kind of problem I needed to worry about."


translate English day7_cr_79d56d24:


    pl "You're so inconsiderate. What if she's worried because of that?"


translate English day7_cr_fbb3f00c:


    sc "It might also be that she doesn't want us to worry."


translate English day7_cr_4f1b3193:


    pl "What? What kind of dumb logic is that?"


translate English day7_cr_3b901b3d:


    sc "She's staying quiet about it because she doesn't want anyone to know, right?{w} All women like keeping secrets."


translate English day7_cr_02d297d5:


    pl "Huh... That means all the women around me are suspicious secret-keepers."


translate English day7_cr_964df7c7:


    pl "That aside, I'm surprised to hear you mention women at all."


translate English day7_cr_f6ae447c:


    sc "What's so strange about it?{w} Everyone has one or two secrets they can't tell others, regardless of their gender."


translate English day7_cr_1ec6a28f:


    pl "Oh? Then you've got a couple too, huh?"


translate English day7_cr_1163ab2b:


    sc "As do you."


translate English day7_cr_c597c45e:


    nar "He raises his face and meets my gaze.{w} I think he's teasing me."


translate English day7_cr_6d28e29b:


    nar "While frustrating, I clam up, unable to respond.{w} This is definitely a secret I can't tell anyone else."


translate English day7_cr_2ab315ab:



    nvl clear
    "{nw}" with sshake


translate English day7_cr_b7a3cb91:


    sc "...[na2], stop for a second."


translate English day7_cr_2985856a:


    pl "What is it...?"


translate English day7_cr_0bcac7a6:


    nar "Securett stops, his gaze directed ahead of us.{w} A low, irregular groaning. A terribly decayed human form.{w} It's one of the Lost."


translate English day7_cr_bfc945d9:


    nar "But it isn't like the ones we've seen before."


translate English day7_cr_49e02e1a:


    nar "It's noticed us, but hasn't attacked us.{w} Instead it just claws around on the ground, crawling."


translate English day7_cr_36884032:


    nar "It's so strange that it covers up my terror."


translate English day7_cr_00ae71cf:


    nar "When I take another look at it, I see a filthy skirt, and something poking out of it.{w} It's a leg. Two legs, both broken in strange directions."


translate English day7_cr_e0599152:


    nar "A simple accident wouldn't have caused that.{w} Someone broke them intentionally."


translate English day7_cr_93b5db56:


    pl "Is that...?"


translate English day7_cr_d0c2f348:


    sc "Some people break the legs of deeply resentful corpses so that they can't chase them if they turn into one of the Lost.{w} It happens from time to time."


translate English day7_cr_5b896186:


    nar "Its low voice comes to my ears.{w} And it sounds somehow colder than the moans of the dead."


translate English day7_cr_5b410373:


    nar "Even after I stop, my eyes and ears continue to accumulate information, until eventually the eerie words begin to line up in my mind."


translate English day7_cr_4375b433:


    nar "In a forest never visited, the corpse of a woman who earned a grudge, killed..."


translate English day7_cr_cba0f13a:


    sc "Don't, [na2]."


translate English day7_cr_28c6ced3:


    nar "Securett stops me from arranging the rest of the words.{w} We were just chatting casually a few moments ago, but now his face was so dark it makes me forget about that."


translate English day7_cr_64a644be:


    sc "We're cleaners.{w} We're not normal priests... and we're most certainly not policemen."


translate English day7_cr_00719d4b:


    sc "Our only job is to dispose of the Lost.{w} We have no authority beyond that."


translate English day7_cr_2bb54f23:


    pl "So you're telling me to ignore seeing an unreasonable crime?{w} How is that moral?"


translate English day7_cr_5ac8bfa4:


    pl "Doesn't the Cleanup Department work for the people's sake?"


translate English day7_cr_d286f85d:


    sc "We do.{w} What I'm trying to tell you is this--always remember your position."


translate English day7_cr_04733d27:


    nar "Securett crosses in front of me and stands in front of the woman.{w} And then, his face pale, he turns back to look at me."


translate English day7_cr_f2d5af05:


    sc "Don't ever forget that."


translate English day7_cr_8d2acd66:


    nar "The wind blows, cutting off his next words."


translate English day7_cr_cabe036b:


    nar "Without any chance for me to ask what he just said, he raises his blade high into the air."


translate English day7_cr_6eaeab6f:



    nvl clear
    "\n After work, I go right back to the dorm.{w} I thought I was used to seeing all the corpses, but when I think of that one crawling on the ground like that, I lose my appetite; I don't end up going to the cafeteria either."


translate English day7_cr_53760ed8:


    "Without meeting anyone on my way back, I just lie down in bed and let my physical exhaustion heal."


translate English day7_cr_7aae8d49:


    et "The words he said at the end won't leave my mind. Always remember your position.{w} That living, moving Lost, that deeply resentful corpse, unable to chase the culprit down... I can't help seeing someone else there."


translate English day7_cr_a52935b8:



    nvl clear
    "\n I probably only remember it so suddenly because the Lost was a woman.{w} I want to stop thinking about it, but the lid on my memories has already popped open.{w} It's showing me the memories of that night whether I want it to or not."


translate English day7_cr_cbfeae22:


    et "But I must not forget about what happened with her.{w} I was scared to remember it.{w} She probably holds more of a grudge towards me than hatred I have for her."


translate English day7_cr_a93fb32e:



    nvl clear
    et "\n \"...Hahaha!\""


translate English day7_cr_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_cr_b1990c90:


    "\n Behind my eyelids, in the darkness, someone laughs.{w} It's a woman's high, seductive laugh, clawing at my eardrums like a sharp, stinging whistle.{w} It's her voice... The voice of the one I forgot."


translate English day7_cr_7eb209c2:


    "Her slick thumb grabs my jaw, and her slender fingers violate me through the gap in my lips.{w} Her powerful hand forces my mouth open.{w} I think at first that it's a shockingly cold human hand, and I only realize that when as it grabs my jaw, its sharp nails dig into my skin."


translate English day7_cr_c7017239:


    et "A slimy fluid flows into my forced-open mouth.{w} I shut my throat; it flows back out of my mouth and down my neck.{w} From the froth I can smell the raw stench of drool, as well as a little bit of saltiness. The choking sensation makes my eyes pop open."


translate English day7_cr_98702c81:



    nvl clear
    "\n And in front of me is her. She covers my body in filthy grease, and she smiles wide enough to split her mouth in two. At some point, I've forgotten what she looks like."


translate English day7_cr_6fbbb92c:


    "After all, her face is shrouded in darkness.{w} But I can see it--in her flowing hair, her smiling mouth, and her eyes."


translate English day7_cr_f6b4b9d0:


    et "Both her blonde hair, which has lost its sheen, and her skin, which has changed color and expanded, press down on my shoulders.{w} In my faint memories, those scarlet eyes alone retain their light, glaring at me..."


translate English day7_cr_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_cr_19be94b4:


    "\n I scream. My eyes fly open again." with sshake


translate English day7_cr_875e88e0:


    "As I open my eyelids, my hazy consciousness clears.{w} I hurriedly look around and see that this is my own room.{w} I'm the only one here. Nobody else but me. Just me."


translate English day7_cr_fa61f7f4:


    et "I tell myself that obvious fact over and over as a form of comfort.{w} And as I repeat it, my body slowly stops shaking."


translate English day7_cr_27666143:



    nvl clear
    "\n Finally, I brush aside my damp bangs and wipe off my cold sweat, taking a deep, frantic breath.{w} Eventually, my clouded mind recalls a calm male voice. I did hear him. I heard the rest of what he said."


translate English day7_cr_3f216a25:


    "It was all because I'd wanted to wipe it from my memories--along with the last moments of that Lost."


translate English day7_cr_8d798f71:


    et "In that final moment, Securett had said this."


translate English day7_cr_09861889:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Don't forget."


translate English day7_cr_a75c14d9:


    et "That sometimes, immorality should be ignored.\""


translate English day7_cr_0a3c1b18:


    nar "Yes. In truth, I'm afraid of women."


translate English day7_cr_673c94f3:


    nar "It was a while ago now, but when I was still new here and didn't know anything, my senior next door had been violent towards me."


translate English day7_cr_56b4d54f:


    nar "If anyone heard this, they'd definitely laugh.{w} But that incident instilled a serious, deadly fear in me."


translate English day7_cr_d84885df:


    nar "After that night, whenever I saw someone female, I would remember the sensation of that woman touching my skin."


translate English day7_cr_49304962:


    nar "The feeling of her five fingers crawling about my skin, her soft tongue deep inside my ear. I can't stand it."


translate English day7_cr_85256270:


    nar "That's when I stopped being able to confront women properly.{w} The scent of perfume, high-pitched laughs, the curves in their bodies..."


translate English day7_cr_800e47e0:


    nar "All of it makes me mad with terror.{w} I understand that they're all human, just like me."


translate English day7_cr_97c52e2d:


    nar "But no matter how I try to deny it, instinctively, women now equal sex in my mind.{w} I'll never be able to have a normal romance again."


translate English day7_cr_bb001255:


    nar "I wouldn't be able to enjoy sex with a lifelong partner.{w} Girls who are friendly to me are a burden I just can't shoulder."


translate English day7_cr_24c1f34a:


    nar "So, so..."


translate English day7_cr_9c938437:


    nar "...I know.{w} These are all just excuses."


translate English day7_cr_a0cdcdc4:


    nar "The sexual act that led to that woman's death is linked to me.{w} In that situation, I could well have refused--but I couldn't bring myself to."


translate English day7_cr_7404f1bd:


    nar "That's the truth of the matter that I've been trying so hard to conceal.{w} It's the same as if I killed her."


translate English day7_cr_dd9ed9be:


    nar "I'd killed someone, and paid for it with only my virginity.{w} I'm terrified of this habit."


translate English day7_cr_f3148251:


    nar "And being scared of this habit, which has made two people into victims now... It's laughable."


translate English day7_cr_4119e8c3:


    nar "I try my best to foster some other kind of emotion inside me, but that terror is something I just can't get rid of."


translate English day7_cr_535866bb:


    nar "Until now, I'd distracted myself from my guilt with loathing, and I'd turned away, too shy to do anything else.{w} But I'm scared of women--scared of sex."


translate English day7_cr_73b5d47a:


    cr "Hello there, Lord [na]!"


translate English day7_cr_c65f42cb:


    nar "I wander aimlessly to the stairwell, where Claire is waiting.{w} Or, well it has to be Claire."


translate English day7_cr_7cbc9af0:


    nar "She's the only one who would be waiting here for me.{w} But her silhouette is so different now that I almost didn't recognize her."


translate English day7_cr_5c89246b:


    pl "...Claire?{w} Did you cut your hair?"


translate English day7_cr_4fb5f6ac:


    cr "Yes! A couple little snips here and there.{w} Hehe. It looks pretty good, doesn't it?"


translate English day7_cr_048bce13:


    pl "A couple little snips... I mean, it looks good, but why the change?"


translate English day7_cr_f9d07942:


    cr "Well, you said something yesterday.{w} About how long hair seems so inconvenient..."


translate English day7_cr_b8d501de:


    cr "Or, rather, that maintaining it must be difficult? Something like that.{w} But you were right--long hair is a huge handful to take care of."


translate English day7_cr_e0cee97c:


    cr "Besides that, though, I originally did my hair like that to show it off to others.{w} But I don't need it anymore."


translate English day7_cr_f7e549b8:


    cr "Because now, I belong only to you!"


translate English day7_cr_e3a03a30:


    nar "Her short hair flutters as she smiles.{w} She's cute, but that just makes it awkward for me."


translate English day7_cr_85854c67:


    nar "With wigs so popular in the capital, basically everyone cuts their hair to sell it.{w} Regardless of gender, long hair is taken as a sign of wealth."


translate English day7_cr_dcfcdb5a:


    nar "And Claire's hair in particular would have been taken care of by many people, including herself, using a lot of energy and money."


translate English day7_cr_95ac68fb:


    nar "\"A couple little snips\" was far too casual a way to describe her decision."


translate English day7_cr_a61fff79:


    pl "Your hair aside... What's the eyepatch for?{w} Did you get hurt?"


translate English day7_cr_98452a09:


    cr "Oh, you mean this?{w} I, well... I suppose I got hurt, yes.{w} It's a little uncomfortable for me to suddenly bring this up."


translate English day7_cr_8a4bea79:


    cr "That is... Well, my fiancé quite enjoys rubbing his member on my stigmata..."


translate English day7_cr_0d0a0312:


    pl "What?{w} Uh...{w} Shit! What the fuck does that mean?!" with sshake


translate English day7_cr_40e963b0:


    cr "Okay, calm down, calm down...{w} It may be unusual back home for you, Lord [na], but it's actually a fairly normal thing to enjoy."


translate English day7_cr_a66edb6b:


    pl "That's not normal! How is it even possible he's sane if he does that?!{w} He can't be sane!"


translate English day7_cr_8b92fd50:


    pl "Then... Then are you blind in that eye now?{w} Shit, I'll kill him... I'll go right there and--" with sshake


translate English day7_cr_8bac22a3:


    nar "Claire gets up and blocks my path.{w} Is she taking HIS side?"


translate English day7_cr_7e1fb770:


    nar "Or does she just not want me prying too much? Either way, it sucks."


translate English day7_cr_cc0fcc0b:


    cr "Please, calm down!{w} He didn't directly touch it or anything so cruel. He just laid it over top of it."


translate English day7_cr_b54198b8:


    cr "It'll be all better tomorrow.{w} Okay?"


translate English day7_cr_a345f78a:


    nar "That horrific explanation naturally does nothing to quell my rage."


translate English day7_cr_56201496:


    nar "But she looks so desperate that I can only back off and sit back down.{w} I sigh."


translate English day7_cr_91052be4:


    nar "Claire looks like she doesn't know what to do, so she gets up from her seat and spins around dramatically."


translate English day7_cr_94889a92:


    cr "Anyway, my hair! Look at my hair!{w} Do you really see it? How do you like it?"


translate English day7_cr_629bf813:


    cr "I'd like an opinion or two.{w} Because I am Clione Myosotis, and I've done this just for you."


translate English day7_cr_1837f0af:


    pl "I mean... I guess I'm more of a short hair kind of guy...{w} But seriously, is this okay with you? It was really long before."


translate English day7_cr_a891f442:


    cr "Whether or not it's \"okay\" with me isn't the issue.{w} I did this for you. It's very light and feels nice."


translate English day7_cr_87d46efd:


    pl "Again, that's not the problem here..."


translate English day7_cr_ddf12e1a:


    nar "Her own mind seems pretty unfocused right now, and saying it was \"for me\" makes me feel bad for some reason."


translate English day7_cr_4807b99c:


    nar "I didn't exactly ask her to do that.{w} But she'd listened to some casual remark I made."


translate English day7_cr_656340c2:


    cr "...Then what is the problem?"


translate English day7_cr_05daca9d:


    pl "Er... Nothing, I was just really surprised at how determined you must have been to suddenly cut your hair!"


translate English day7_cr_67cdae82:


    pl "I'm just happy that you like it.{w} And it really does look good on you."


translate English day7_cr_0cd24a90:


    cr "Tee hee! If there's anything more you wish of me in the future, please say so anytime.{w} I would do anything for our love."


translate English day7_cr_ffc3ab0e:


    pl "Ha ha... Aren't you forgetting something, little missy?{w} I'm flattered you want to do things for me, but you should prioritize what YOU want to do first and foremost."


translate English day7_cr_3e8cd462:


    cr "Oh, of course I understand that. No need to worry.{w} Because doing things for you is the same as doing things for myself!"


translate English day7_cr_4d0d3bc5:


    cr "Making you happy gives me joy, Lord [na]."


translate English day7_cr_53a39a72:


    nar "Heat naturally rises to my face as I remember what happened yesterday."


translate English day7_cr_3cc88e16:


    nar "And that's not from excitement or awkwardness--it's from pure shame. And that fact makes me even more embarrassed. I hang my head."


translate English day7_cr_7d089a26:


    nar "It's not that I hate her now. Her shorter hair goes really well with her bright personality. It's cute, and hearing her cheerful voice calms me down."


translate English day7_cr_c125dcb8:


    nar "But I can't properly respond to those emotions--and that's an issue."


translate English day7_cr_fd3b91f0:


    pl "Did you get home alright yesterday?"


translate English day7_cr_a43f4e3e:


    cr "Yes, thanks to you. Well, perhaps I shouldn't say that.{w} Getting the clothes I'd borrowed dirty earned me some anger."


translate English day7_cr_44253715:


    pl "That's why I said that they'd get angry. I hate to say I told you so."


translate English day7_cr_fb610870:


    cr "Oh... How can you say \"I told you so\" to a lover after seeing another bruise on their body?"


translate English day7_cr_8e638779:


    pl "...But I did say they'd be mad with you."


translate English day7_cr_92faccaf:


    cr "And there you go, getting all gloomy again.{w} Don't be so sad!"


translate English day7_cr_fb5dc520:


    cr "I'm here now, and yesterday was the greatest day of my life."


translate English day7_cr_502cf5ee:


    pl "Mm..."


translate English day7_cr_bc7dbeed:


    cr "What a dreary response.{w} You know, I may begin to sulk if you don't start giving me more active reactions!"


translate English day7_cr_8cba139d:


    cr "A girl's patience only lasts so long, after all."


translate English day7_cr_37f465ff:


