    pl "Of course I don't!{w} How the hell could I understand your feelings?" with sshake


translate English day8_cr_24df53bc:


    pl "You didn't do anything until now, and now you're yelling at me? It doesn't make sense!"


translate English day8_cr_42ccb5af:


    nar "Grette catches her breath and frowns.{w} I think she's about to get really angry at me, but it's actually the opposite."


translate English day8_cr_c010d456:


    nar "She looks like she wants to keep playing this role.{w} Naturally, I can't stand that attitude."


translate English day8_cr_24d51d37:


    nar "She hides behind her excuses of \"adult responsibilities,\" anxious and afraid.{w} And now she looks like she's about to cry."


translate English day8_cr_4835343e:


    gr "...I understand why you feel the need to blame me.{w} You can't process your emotions without blaming it on someone else."


translate English day8_cr_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day8_cr_825347a9:


    gr "But you have to understand this, [na2]. There is still nothing that can be changed.{w} This is happening in her private family life--it has nothing to do with the temple."


translate English day8_cr_a650cdab:


    gr "So if Claire doesn't wish for this to be resolved, then we can't meddle in her affairs."


translate English day8_cr_8df64f82:


    pl "Isn't it your job to do something about that?!" with sshake


translate English day8_cr_77ba1410:


    nar "I punch the bookshelf with a fist, but it doesn't reduce my anger."


translate English day8_cr_446edc21:


    nar "Grette pales to the point where her face looks almost gray, looking astonished at the papers flying off the shelf."


translate English day8_cr_22e08221:


    nar "It looks like she has nothing else left to say."


translate English day8_cr_22b1f5ef:


    gr "...Yes. It's all my fault."


translate English day8_cr_6b7df6c0:


    nar "Those words don't sound like a reply to me--they sound like she's telling them to herself."


translate English day8_cr_03d76520:


    nar "She holds a hand to her head as if dizzy and shivers, but I ignore her and burst out of the room."


translate English day8_cr_70095aac:


    nar "Seeing her like that is unpleasant. It's like she's pretending to be a mother who just heard of her daughter's death."


translate English day8_cr_d507a019:


    nar "After leaving the infirmary, I wander around the temple for a long while, but it doesn't do much to calm me down."


translate English day8_cr_33bf3c70:


    nar "I didn't realize it until actually seeing Grette, but I can't do anything but hate all the adults around Claire."


translate English day8_cr_5d78f7ca:


    nar "They had the power to help her, and yet they all watched and caused the worst to come to pass.{w} They deprived her of a place to go."


translate English day8_cr_ecfbe7b8:


    nar "And in the end, they try to level the responsibility on me. I hate them.{w} Seeing them feel a little guilt, like that woman, just isn't enough."


translate English day8_cr_f5b88cc5:


    nar "She should be ashamed of herself for the rest of her life.{w} The rest of her life."


translate English day8_cr_c5e84bd3:


    nar "In the end, I don't see Claire today.{w} I went to the stairwell, but she was nowhere to be found."


translate English day8_cr_07193778:


    nar "She seemed to be pushing herself to come to the temple for the last few days. I wonder if something happened.{w} My worries turn into anxiety and set me on edge."


translate English day8_cr_40b6a0f9:


    nar "Those bruises I've seen so often come back to mind.{w} Maybe something terrible is being done to her again."


translate English day8_cr_66aa8a85:


    nar "My heart sinks at the thought.{w} I can hear my pulse pounding in my ears."


translate English day8_cr_58c0b211:


    nar "I have to make sure she's okay.{w} She has to promise me she'll see me again tomorrow with a smile."


translate English day8_cr_0ea60114:


    nar "Remembering there's a phone in the back of the dorm, I go over that way.{w} I'm worried I might overhear someone else's conversation."


translate English day8_cr_04fa04d5:


    nar "But it's afternoon now, and all the idle priests have gotten to work on their tasks."


translate English day8_cr_ad409c8f:


    nar "Still, I do actually find a familiar face there.{w} It's Maya, who I haven't seen all day, talking to someone on the phone as she twists the cord around her finger."


translate English day8_cr_86a0ce1d:


    nar "Her expression and voice are sullen as usual, but just seeing her having a conversation with someone I don't see makes me feel pretty awkward."


translate English day8_cr_5dda46a4:


    my "Mm-hmm...{w} Yeah...{w} No."


translate English day8_cr_88d7ecaf:


    nar "Even when I get close enough to hear her, all she does is repeat a bunch of short answers before lowering the receiver."


translate English day8_cr_8ccb5647:


    nar "Then she lowers her eyes, as if reminiscing on the conversation.{w} A few moments later, she notices me and turns."


translate English day8_cr_94a6267a:


    my "...Oh, [na2].{w} I'm sorry. How long have you been there?"


translate English day8_cr_2ec04fc0:


    pl "I just got here, actually. Didn't think I'd bump into you.{w} Oh, and I didn't hear anything you were talking about, so don't worry."


translate English day8_cr_c16194c2:


    my "Y-You really didn't hear anything, right?"


translate English day8_cr_0b034c9c:


    pl "I didn't! Who were you talking to?"


translate English day8_cr_6feae23c:


    my "Umm... It was Claire.{w} She didn't come at all today, so I got worried..."


translate English day8_cr_6a0ac5f8:


    pl "Really! I came here to talk to her too.{w} Did she say she's alright?"


translate English day8_cr_7858b673:


    my "Mm-hmm. Apparently it's nothing major.{w} But... Apparently she had to make a promise with her parents."


translate English day8_cr_dbdfc4e8:


    my "And since she didn't come today, she'll be here first thing tomorrow morning."


translate English day8_cr_5afbac1b:


    nar "Maya is unusually forthcoming with her answers; maybe she realizes I'm worried about Claire."


translate English day8_cr_31935998:


    nar "The relief causes my mood to finally relax.{w} It's not only because I know Claire's safe, either."


translate English day8_cr_339fd358:


    nar "It's also because I have a friend to talk to in Maya."


translate English day8_cr_8701f6b9:


    nar "When she looks away from my gaze, I get anxious.{w} Does she know Claire's secret after all?"


translate English day8_cr_5ad12c67:


    nar "I really want to ask her, but I'm sure it'll make me upset again, so I try to think of something else."


translate English day8_cr_a97f827d:


    pl "You were working by yourself today, right, Maya?{w} Anything out of the ordinary happen?"


translate English day8_cr_838de37a:


    my "No, I was fine.{w} I don't do very out of the ordinary jobs anyway..."


translate English day8_cr_a6911d9e:


    pl "What kind of stuff do you do?"


translate English day8_cr_7645e656:


    my "Pick up trash and other things..."


translate English day8_cr_5a609d31:


    pl "Hey, that's a good job, though.{w} Without people like you, the capital would be a huge pile of garbage right now!{w} You did a good thing."


translate English day8_cr_e6cfeb6c:


    my "Aw, thanks... Oh. {w} What happened yesterday, [na2]? You were with Cue for work, right?"


translate English day8_cr_a4501c5a:


    pl "Oh, yeah, I did.{w} The days have been so long lately that even after a night's sleep, I've been kinda careless."


translate English day8_cr_4d22963a:


    nar "I try to think of something else, but nothing comes to mind.{w} It's been like this constantly for me."


translate English day8_cr_492a64f8:


    nar "I've been spending most of my days with Claire, who gladly carries on the conversation even if I can't."


translate English day8_cr_e7120c32:


    pl "...Oh, right. Something weird happened when I was with him."


translate English day8_cr_47d09996:


    my "Something weird?"


translate English day8_cr_88dbc15a:


    pl "How should I put it...{w} We saw one of the Lost that seemed to be involved in a strange incident."


translate English day8_cr_326a9067:


    pl "He disposed of it anyway, saying sometimes you have to ignore it."


translate English day8_cr_ff70f8de:


    pl "I'm not trying to pass secrets around or anything, y'know?{w} But I was just thinking that Securett can be really calm about problems like those."


translate English day8_cr_6c522113:


    my "Mm..."


translate English day8_cr_0e9ad1b0:


    pl "Mm?"


translate English day8_cr_16c1aaca:


    my "Well... I wasn't there, so I can't say for sure..."


translate English day8_cr_ccfae97c:


    my "But I don't think Cue would ignore a person in need..."


translate English day8_cr_e7acab70:


    my "I think maybe he meant to say not to get involved with something you won't be able to take responsibility for..."


translate English day8_cr_de080c95:


    pl "Hmm..."


translate English day8_cr_b2fe832f:


    my "...S-Sorry.{w} I shouldn't be making guesses like that..."


translate English day8_cr_f7a2fb48:


    pl "No, no, I was just thinking about how something like this happened before, too."


translate English day8_cr_bb998c01:


    pl "Am I being too meddlesome without really understanding what I'm getting into?"


translate English day8_cr_f7738cf3:


    my "N-No, I don't think so..."


translate English day8_cr_ac686ee2:


    pl "Either way, I'm kinda jealous of Cue having you on his side!"


translate English day8_cr_e1ed8ce6:


    my "I-it's not about being on his side, or one of you being right or wrong, or any of that!"


translate English day8_cr_d69767f4:


    my "I can understand where you're coming from too, [na2].{w} In fact, I think your mindset is more normal..."


translate English day8_cr_c1dd2adb:


    my "But Cue has been working for longer than we have, and he has more experience, so... Well..."


translate English day8_cr_0e518dba:


    nar "I haven't seen Maya this flustered in a while.{w} I get what she's trying to say, though."


translate English day8_cr_087c364c:


    nar "Both of them are right on all counts--but that doesn't mean my own viewpoint is wrong.{w} Just that the situation didn't call for it."


translate English day8_cr_816afe76:


    nar "The boomerang he threw at me when he told me to remember my place is coming around and whacking me in the head again."


translate English day8_cr_90cd9868:


    pl "Anyway, leaving that aside.{w} Do you use the phone often?"


translate English day8_cr_52fd85a9:


    my "Every once in a while, I guess... When I remember."


translate English day8_cr_b0f080f6:


    my "We can't leave the temple at all during work, so sometimes I get sad when I hear things about the outside."


translate English day8_cr_697c5d3e:


    pl "Oh... I kinda get that."


translate English day8_cr_8b9bf18e:


    my "Really? Maybe we're similar in a few ways...{w} Did you come here to call Claire, by any chance?"


translate English day8_cr_72dfdf53:


    pl "Oh... Yeah. I just got her number yesterday."


translate English day8_cr_0704b55a:


    pl "She said that now that a lady gave me her number, I should make sure to call her once per day, or something."


translate English day8_cr_3d9fbbb0:


    my "Ahaha... You two are really good friends, huh..."


translate English day8_cr_ceaccc32:


    pl "So are you, Maya.{w} You got to the phone before I did.{w} Although I heard you two talk almost every day."


translate English day8_cr_5ac03a29:


    my "I, um...{w} I don't. Claire is just forcing herself to be nice to me."


translate English day8_cr_a28c668b:


    my "Once I get a little more busy, she'll get tired of the boring commoner she can't see eye to eye with..."


translate English day8_cr_ee7d9ee4:


    pl "Come on, don't say stuff like that.{w} I've been wondering--why do you always get so daunted when Claire comes up?"


translate English day8_cr_71ce62d6:


    my "Well, that's... Claire's younger than me, but she's smarter, and good at talking, and I just think she's great, so..."


translate English day8_cr_36c4322b:


    pl "You're right about that, but..."


translate English day8_cr_255c7e99:


    my "...I'm jealous of her.{w} Even without the pretty face, or her skills..."


translate English day8_cr_2ba00d1e:


    my "She never hides what she's thinking, so whenever we talk... This is really embarrassing, I know, but..."


translate English day8_cr_22ff4ed2:


    my "I just get jealous of her."


translate English day8_cr_bf02e313:


    nar "She seems to be at a loss for words for some reason.{w} It's not because she doesn't want to talk about her."


translate English day8_cr_7cd9278f:


    nar "In fact, it's as though my heart is being weirdly drawn to her reserved confession.{w} I still don't know why."


translate English day8_cr_f3751fec:


    nar "And I get the feeling that maybe I'm not really supposed to."


translate English day8_cr_70c84821:


    my "And, I guess... When you're with her, you seem like you're really having fun..."


translate English day8_cr_174982b7:


    pl "Oh..."


translate English day8_cr_db6b8f32:


    nar "I can't simply tell her my feelings, so I give her a one-word reply.{w} She nods once to me in response."


translate English day8_cr_53b7aba6:


    nar "Her smile truly does make me feel like she knows everything I'm thinking."


translate English day8_cr_d2eac319:


    my "But I know I shouldn't be thinking like that..."


translate English day8_cr_e1799e94:


    nar "Then she walks away without so much as a good-bye and goes up the stairs."


translate English day8_cr_656aa740:


    nar "She told me what she's feeling right now.{w} So maybe I should have confessed my sin to her too."


translate English day8_cr_688eeb3c:


    nar "But I can neither call out to stop her nor go after her."


translate English day8_cr_0f9648f8:


    nar "After all, I haven't gotten my once-a-day conversation with Claire over with yet."


translate English day8_cr_715cf326:


    nar "I open the crumpled piece of paper, my fingers trembling as I punch in her number.{w} The receiver touching my ear is heavy for something to be held in one hand, and cold."


translate English day8_cr_c3a45515:


    nar "In the silence, I remember all of the things Maya just told me."


translate English day8_cr_82527a8b:


    nar "Do I envy Claire just like she does?{w} No."


translate English day8_cr_da64ad8f:


    nar "Maya may be in a similar situation, but there's no reason for me to envy her.{w} There must be another reason."


translate English day8_cr_5ee98594:


    cr "Hello, this is Clione."


translate English day8_cr_8ffae7ff:


    nar "When I hear her voice over the receiver, I immediately hesitate over what to say, especially since I can't see her face."


translate English day8_cr_a94f5d61:


    nar "As I struggle to find a few words of greeting, Claire speaks again."


translate English day8_cr_53876ef1:


    cr "Hello?"


translate English day8_cr_e338dd7b:


    pl "Oh, um, hello. It's me."


translate English day8_cr_3a8ddf8f:


    cr "Oh! Lord [na]?{w} I didn't think you'd actually call me. I suppose not seeing you all day has borne fruit."


translate English day8_cr_308cd605:


    pl "What are you talking about?{w} You're the one making me do this..."


translate English day8_cr_1675c540:


    cr "Tee hee. I'm just happy, that's all.{w} How was your day?"


translate English day8_cr_fcc704af:


    pl "Eh, it was alright."


translate English day8_cr_c4c098c8:


    cr "Oh, come, now... You've no sense at all of how to speak to a lover, as usual."


translate English day8_cr_ece4cdc4:


    cr "You're supposed to say you lost the will to live, not being able to see your beloved Claire's face for an entire day!"


translate English day8_cr_d3ca5f3a:


    pl "Actually, that might be close to the mark."


translate English day8_cr_43bef6dd:


    cr "Wow! Truly?"


translate English day8_cr_aefcd91a:


    pl "Yeah. I'm serious. I was pretty worried, not seeing you all day.{w} It's like you said--I didn't have much will to live."


translate English day8_cr_4adde141:


    pl "If you're not going to be able to come anymore, I wish you'd say something in advance."


translate English day8_cr_e86d54fa:


    cr "Oh my, oh my... That makes me happy."


translate English day8_cr_63193444:


    pl "What? Why?"


translate English day8_cr_513268bd:


    cr "I hope you'll worry over me even more in the future, Lord [na]."


translate English day8_cr_7c761180:


    pl "Haha. Putting on the spoiled brat routine a little fast there, aren't you?"


translate English day8_cr_cfa59952:


    cr "My presence in your daily thoughts proves that I now occupy part of your life, Lord [na]."


translate English day8_cr_47aab6cf:


    cr "So yes, I'd like you to give me even more thought."


translate English day8_cr_de080c95_1:


    pl "Hrm..."


translate English day8_cr_5db7c75c:


    cr "Hehe. I suppose that was an embarrassing thing to say."


translate English day8_cr_a1da29b4:


    pl "It's not that, it's more like..."


translate English day8_cr_1bba9dac:


    pl "Oh, right. Is it true you're not a reserve priest anymore?"


translate English day8_cr_5bc2751d:


    cr "Unfortunately, yes.{w} It won't be possible to break off the engagement immediately, so..."


translate English day8_cr_8c526430:


    cr "But even if I weren't in this situation, I would have ended up marrying you anyway.{w} And then I still couldn't have become a priest."


translate English day8_cr_7b29b9a7:


    cr "And that would cause problems for you continuing your job there, too."


translate English day8_cr_a26c4ba2:


    cr "So, while you're working away at the temple, I must make preparations here in the outside world for the marriage!"


translate English day8_cr_b203f5c8:


    nar "Whenever Claire describes her feelings like this, I always feel like something's off."


translate English day8_cr_02b274aa:


    nar "This time, that feeling turns into a question and leaves my mouth before I can stop it."


translate English day8_cr_b30c13b9:


    pl "Hey, I'm just asking because I'm curious, but..."


translate English day8_cr_29181e5a:


    pl "Now that you feel like there's an issue with your and your fiance's relationship, you're seeking to break your engagement with him because you fell in love with me, right?"


translate English day8_cr_aeee47f9:


    pl "What do you think you would have done if you hadn't fallen in love with me?"


translate English day8_cr_69786a76:


    cr "That's an odd question to ask.{w} I would probably be living a life as an obedient, docile little wife to my fiancé right now."


translate English day8_cr_5cbf7343:


    cr "I actually decided I'd do just that if you were to reject my confession.{w} If the whole engagement was already broken off, then, hmm..."


translate English day8_cr_63703133:


    cr "Ah, I suppose I would have gone looking for other encounters."


translate English day8_cr_b5b25e9f:


    pl "Why's that?"


translate English day8_cr_aac044e5:


    cr "What do you mean?"


translate English day8_cr_1d7584f7:


    pl "Well, it's just that... I don't really get how it connects to marriage.{w} Do you just... feel like you have to be in love, or whatever?"


translate English day8_cr_ea1de805:


    cr "What?{w} Ahaha! Lord [na], you truly don't understand."


translate English day8_cr_0d510207:


    cr "Who, in these times, could get by without getting married?{w} We live in a world where not having a lover is a cause for embarrassment."


translate English day8_cr_980d3b25:


    cr "People talk a lot about how only lives with love are worth living, and so you would be missing out by not falling in love."


translate English day8_cr_98ec5b36:


    pl "Wait. Then do people go out with guys just to brag about it to others?"


translate English day8_cr_a93f9219:


    cr "Well, not necessarily.{w} They're good chances to improve yourself, too."


translate English day8_cr_f9460d6d:


    pl "No, like, I mean, would anyone do? Just as long as they were affectionate to you?"


translate English day8_cr_5cdee298:


    nar "There's silence for a moment.{w} Her voice lowers as she says her next words."


translate English day8_cr_4026dc78:


    cr "Lord [na], you speak as though you treat me with affection."


translate English day8_cr_5f5bf843:


    pl "What? No, that's not what I was trying to get at--"


translate English day8_cr_1a7f31c0:


    cr "Then I'm wrong? About what?!{w} Have you ever really even paid attention to me?!" with sshake


translate English day8_cr_95be2744:


    cr "It's even more difficult for ME to understand!" with sshake


translate English day8_cr_5354ed19:


    nar "My mind goes blank for a moment as she lashes out."


translate English day8_cr_e2952e0c:


    nar "I'd been swimming in all sorts of different thoughts, but hearing her shriek cools my head."


translate English day8_cr_ae840eeb:


    nar "I feel like none of this was really necessary.{w} And that brings this morning back to mind."


translate English day8_cr_952b59c4:


    pl "...Look, it's my fault. Sorry about that."


translate English day8_cr_7b543af8:


    pl "I should have realized you might have a different way of thinking from me.{w} I'm trying my best too. I'm really sorry."


translate English day8_cr_d7ead5c7:


    cr "...No, I apologize. It's my fault."


translate English day8_cr_e1811f78:


    pl "No, it's not..."


translate English day8_cr_cf573367:


    cr "I don't understand how I can be this foolish and this unable to choose my words properly."


translate English day8_cr_e89a156f:


    cr "This is why I embarrass people.{w} I'm no good. I just make others angry."


translate English day8_cr_dc06f524:


    nar "With a diffident voice, Claire begins to blame herself, just like I was worried she might.{w} I feel my heart grow heavier every time she deprecates herself."


translate English day8_cr_a840f633:


    pl "Seriously, that's not true. Stop saying that!{w} Don't try to justify the violence others inflict on you like that."


translate English day8_cr_15c476f4:


    cr "......"


translate English day8_cr_330d4269:


    pl "I was the one who said something he shouldn't have anyway."


translate English day8_cr_be9a4b0d:


    cr "I would... I'd rather we not raise our voices when we fight... It's very sad to think about."


translate English day8_cr_225f6644:


    cr "And it scares me. It reminds me of my current fiancé."


translate English day8_cr_37236b00:


    pl "I didn't want to raise my voice either...{w} Sigh. I'm just saying weird stuff at this point. I'm going to head to bed."


translate English day8_cr_618a1e73:


    pl "I'm pretty tired from work.{w} I probably shouldn't have called you when I feel like this."


translate English day8_cr_32ffaaab:


    cr "Ah... You don't need to worry about that.{w} I was being truthful when I said I was happy to hear your voice... I'll go to sleep soon myself."


translate English day8_cr_75cd9bbe:


    cr "Good night, Lord [na]!{w} I love you."


translate English day8_cr_39fe4c1d:


    pl "Good night, Claire."


translate English day8_cr_e436ef7d:


    nar "When I hang up and realize I won't hear Claire's voice in my ear, I feel regret settling over me again."


translate English day8_cr_8d134927:


    nar "Before, I had so much fun talking to her.{w} We had a common interest, and she seemed like the only person I could really talk to."


translate English day8_cr_64e23dbd:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'd completely forgotten about that fact until Maya reminded me.{w} When was the last time I had a good time talking to Claire? I'm pretty sure it was just a couple days ago, but it feels like so long in the past."


translate English day8_cr_83627a4b:


    "Why did Claire come to love me? Was she just misunderstanding her feelings from the beginning?{w} What does it mean to love someone, anyway?"


translate English day8_cr_2d2f3aa1:


    "Is there any reason to fall in love with someone if you're not after something like money or the easing of lust?{w} Is it really so much fun to share something so awkward with another person without expecting anything in return?"


translate English day8_cr_f5fb5510:


    et "Being together without thinking about anything?{w} Talking without having a reason to?{w} Is that stuff really normal? It seems pretty abnormal to me, like some kind of weird, twisted lover."


translate English day8_cr_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_cr_954fdf78:


    et "\n \"Good night, Lord [na]! I love you.\""


translate English day8_cr_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_cr_5630ea30:


    "\n No... I don't have to think that hard about it. I actually love her too, don't I?{w} These feelings I have for her--other people would easily just call it love, wouldn't they?{w} Yeah. That has to be it!"


translate English day8_cr_172199e0:


    "I want to call her again to tell her that, but it won't happen.{w} Because I know it's still too early to do nighttime greetings.{w} Asking something like, \"Do you sleep right after eating dinner?\" would only bother both of us.{w} I'll tell her this tomorrow."


translate English day8_cr_5adb9388:


    et "Because I've decided that I love her."


translate English day8_cr_33eca423:


    et "A shadow falls over the passage. I hear the voices of other priests.{w} \"She\" isn't here--the one who would listen to my confession.{w} Alone, I look back on my mistakes, and I just end up feeling more miserable."


translate English day8_cr_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_0ccd3fa2:



    nvl clear
    "\n After finishing my call with Claire, I don't encounter anyone else."


translate English day9_cr_dd6d20ba:


    "The depression is making me hungry, so I wander over to the cafeteria for some food, then head back to my room and lie down."


translate English day9_cr_2051b60c:


    et "I only ate a little bit of leftover bread, but it felt like stealing, since nobody else was in the cafeteria at the time."


translate English day9_cr_2b6b44ec:



    nvl clear
    "\n In my dream, I don't see the usual angel. Instead, I see Claire."


translate English day9_cr_70b22972:


    "In the dream, we're not sitting atop entrails or a cold staircase.{w} Instead, we're in a tea shop in town, and not acting like a couple--not holding hands or pressing lips together."


translate English day9_cr_afce75cc:


    "I don't need to whisper my love to her, and she doesn't want me to in the first place."


translate English day9_cr_e870cdfb:


    "We just talk and talk, our empty cups in front of us.{w} We don't do anything else."


translate English day9_cr_fec1ed43:



    nvl clear
    et "\n Her voice in the dream is as clear and bright as a sunny sky, and even after I awaken from the dream, I have trouble believing this wretched place where I currently am is even reality."


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_e1e18999:


    "\n But the dreamscape fades, in the end, the dim midnight sun welcoming in a new morning."


translate English day9_cr_e459a54b:


    nar "I thought I left early, taking only what I needed, but the room sounds noisy, like I made it just in time for roll call."


translate English day9_cr_c1664f08:


    nar "It's not normally this lively in here before the bishop arrives, but today's it's awfully loud."


translate English day9_cr_65d75370:


    nar "I've experienced this sort of thing before.{w} That sharp, high-pitched voice I hear once in a while coming from people chatting happily."


translate English day9_cr_7e937410:


    nar "A conversation centered around a single player.{w} It's proof that a special guest has come."


translate English day9_cr_704e660b:


    cr "Oh, you're here!"


translate English day9_cr_0a2c20d0:


    nar "After hurrying to open the door, the high voice's owner breaks away from the crowd and approaches me."


translate English day9_cr_42f31fc3:


    nar "Their conversation cuts off, but it isn't followed with silence."


translate English day9_cr_e7442bc4:


    nar "Everyone continues their own, smaller conversations, though they're still looking at me."


translate English day9_cr_1baae580:


    nar "The only one who falls quiet is Maya.{w} I'd guess she was talking to Claire before I got here too."


translate English day9_cr_08d2e18a:


    nar "Like the others, Maya turns her gaze to me, then immediately hangs her head."


translate English day9_cr_43c60078:


    pl "Claire..."


translate English day9_cr_38b6f2ea:


    nar "I say her name out of reflex--then immediately realize that was a mistake.{w} Doubtful eyes like thorns pierce into me."


translate English day9_cr_6b71eda2:


    pl "Hey, it's Claire!{w} Ha ha. You here to resupply again already?"


translate English day9_cr_e51c25d0:


    cr "No, not exactly."


translate English day9_cr_975d3e19:


    nar "Claire tilts her head a little, but answers with a smile."


translate English day9_cr_39a9c66a:


    cr "I've come to see you.{w} Did I not mention it yesterday? How I'd come early today, since yesterday we couldn't see each other at all."


translate English day9_cr_a8e781eb:


    pl "Huh?{w} W-Wait, that's the first I've heard of it!"


translate English day9_cr_2d0eb447:


    cr "Oh, then...{w} Ah! Perhaps I told Maya this, and not you."


translate English day9_cr_db95df8b:


    pl "Right? Gotta get your head on straight..."


translate English day9_cr_c3a3f019:


    cr "Hee hee. It's fine. I'm here, and that's what matters.{w} I was worried you might be late again today."


translate English day9_cr_43913d5c:


    cr "But to come this early in the morning without hearing anything...{w} There must be something connecting us. Isn't there?"


translate English day9_cr_386dd777:


    nar "She can prod all she wants, but how am I supposed to give her a straight answer in this situation?"


translate English day9_cr_de385c09:


    nar "She's the one who keeps going on about this secret romance or whatever.{w} But she doesn't seem to want to hide it at all."


translate English day9_cr_068cbb96:


    nar "I hear laughter from behind her as someone begins to whisper to someone else, too low for me to hear."


translate English day9_cr_99d29f25:


    nar "One of them should be asking her a question directly now.{w} Whatever that question means..."


translate English day9_cr_91726b49:


    nar "I'm sure Claire will nod and agree.{w} Or maybe she'll engage in some light banter first."


translate English day9_cr_06008029:


    pl "Hey, Claire--"


translate English day9_cr_48d957a7:


    my "What do you mean, you came to see [na2]?"


translate English day9_cr_5423e3dc:


    nar "Suddenly, Maya stands up from her seat.{w} I look over to her, but strangely, she won't meet my gaze."


translate English day9_cr_2024e55d:


    nar "With everyone else looking on, Maya watches Claire."


translate English day9_cr_1b4861ac:


    my "Were you two always this close?{w} Just stop. It's too early for this... And everyone is here..."


translate English day9_cr_2c6c2d01:


    my "You're bothering [na2]."


translate English day9_cr_19ca05a4:


    cr "Maya, what in the world has gotten into you?{w} You should already know that we're friends..."


translate English day9_cr_bf9b93e2:


    nar "Claire's voice is shaking.{w} Her smile is gone, too, like she can't figure out what's going on all of a sudden."


translate English day9_cr_67dfa014:


    nar "Ignoring her reaction, Maya keeps her hands together and looks at us closely."


translate English day9_cr_8a898c0d:


    my "Are you two... well, going out?"


translate English day9_cr_b980ae45:


    pl "N-No!" with sshake


translate English day9_cr_15d6cf8e:


    nar "I accidentally raise my voice.{w} Taking a step forward, I feel like I can hear Maya's ragged breathing."


translate English day9_cr_dbb69ef5:


    nar "She squeezes her hands painfully tightly and uses only her eyes to glare at me."


translate English day9_cr_5568f7e9:


    my "Oh?{w} So that's what you think, [na2]...{w} But what about you, Claire?"


translate English day9_cr_dac6741e:


    cr "I, I...!{w} We're..."


translate English day9_cr_30b5a6e8:


    nar "Claire falls silent.{w} The moment I see her head begin to hang, I grab her limp hand."


translate English day9_cr_59aa694e:


    nar "The door's still open, so I run out of the room."


translate English day9_cr_46ad3d91:


    my "You're leaving together?{w} You'll regret it!"


translate English day9_cr_46057e13:


    my "Wait, come on...!!!" with sshake


translate English day9_cr_bacc333b:


    nar "Maya's been holding these yells in for a long time, but she doesn't come after us."


translate English day9_cr_2d62a714:


    nar "But I keep running anyway, desperate to get away from that sound."


translate English day9_cr_609223b7:


    nar "Cheers, whistles, and loud laughter drown out Maya's trembling voice, making me dizzy."


translate English day9_cr_a6f4d776:


    nar "Why did it come to this?{w} What just happened?"


translate English day9_cr_7525a91c:


    nar "As I run to try and shake off my confusion, I suddenly feel the hand I'm holding begin to pull at me."


translate English day9_cr_651de20f:


    nar "That sensation makes me realize I'm not alone right now."


translate English day9_cr_4339c980:


    cr "Please, wait... How far do you intend on going?!"


translate English day9_cr_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_cr_df672563:


    cr "You took me outside, despite all the people nearby..."


translate English day9_cr_fc8885a7:


    cr "Don't you know the Cleanup Department priests love spreading rumors?"


translate English day9_cr_223d82dd:


    cr "I just don't understand why you did this..."


translate English day9_cr_4c461a39:


    pl "I could ask you the same thing.{w} Weren't you the one who said we were keeping our relationship a secret?"


translate English day9_cr_3633cdba:


    pl "So what was all that? Why didn't you say no?"


translate English day9_cr_92d46bf4:


    cr "Well...{w} I'm sorry. I made a mistake."


translate English day9_cr_89af64ad:


    pl "You're right--all those priests were watching us, and now it's all weird."


translate English day9_cr_dcabe3bc:


    pl "And now that you couldn't give them an answer, what do you think they'll all think of us now?!"


translate English day9_cr_b9c33fb0:


    cr "But... I...{w} I just didn't want to deny our relationship while others were listening."


translate English day9_cr_68c5b442:


    cr "Logically, I knew I should have, but I just couldn't!{w} I'm not always calm about this like you are, Lord [na]!"


translate English day9_cr_3052044b:


    pl "I... But that's not..."


translate English day9_cr_fc59a74c:


    cr "Speech is a transformation of thoughts into words.{w} Words have power, and the ones you speak to others become truth."


translate English day9_cr_7bcfefdc:


    cr "I don't...{w} I don't want that. It scares me!"


translate English day9_cr_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_cr_500790ef:


    nar "I release her hand and sigh.{w} I wasn't scolding her--the situation is just tiring me out."


translate English day9_cr_fdfeaf94:


    nar "We walk a little more, heading for the stairwell again."


translate English day9_cr_275e8a0b:


    nar "Everyone else is busy getting ready for work, so we're the only ones walking about the temple.{w} Nobody gets in our way."


translate English day9_cr_083d352b:


    nar "But we're heading for the stairwell because it's cramped and dark--the sort of place we can relax in this vast temple."


translate English day9_cr_5621ed75:


    nar "We don't talk on the way there, but I could tell Claire is thinking about something."


translate English day9_cr_c96cbbc8:


    pl "Hey..."


translate English day9_cr_6316a902:


    cr "Yes?"


translate English day9_cr_f6fa522c:


    pl "I heard you weren't an apprentice priest anymore.{w} What's your excuse for coming to the temple every day?"


translate English day9_cr_2f40f0dc:


    cr "I don't exactly have some excuse I'm using to gain entry to the temple."


translate English day9_cr_ed5de9db:


    cr "It's just...{w} I'm free to do with my time what I please, right? In essence, I'm sneaking in."


translate English day9_cr_cc568a6b:


    pl "Sneaking in?"


translate English day9_cr_36b4ed73:


    nar "Considering her situation, coming to the temple without permission was very risky."


translate English day9_cr_8bd8877c:


    nar "If anyone found out, she was sure to be punished again."


translate English day9_cr_1305aff8:


    nar "Now what was I supposed to do about that..."


translate English day9_cr_d3bcd73d:


    cr "Um, Lord [na].{w} Before we reflect on what just happened, I'd first like to offer my apologies."


translate English day9_cr_2de24bb8:


    pl "Your apologies?"


translate English day9_cr_c1d1bb09:


    cr "My thoughtless words last night fouled your mood.{w} I want to apologize for that again."


translate English day9_cr_629eaa2d:


    cr "I'm very sorry for ruining the one connection we had yesterday."


translate English day9_cr_fb703e48:


    pl "It's fine. I was just a little surprised.{w} World's full of all different sorts."


translate English day9_cr_3c0b8c36:


    pl "I'm bound not to understand plenty of them, right?{w} You're one of them--that's all."


translate English day9_cr_8efaa5b4:


    cr "No, that will not do!{w} We are already lovers, and we must live our two lives as one."


translate English day9_cr_f58cd767:


    cr "If we don't strive to understand the other's thoughts and feelings, incidents like last night's will surely happen again."


translate English day9_cr_2b1998f0:


    cr "So let us talk! We lack experience in these little heart-to-hearts."


translate English day9_cr_2e190b3b:


    nar "Heart-to-hearts? How can she suggest that when she has no idea what I'm going to say?{w} Even I don't know what I'll say."


translate English day9_cr_3ce5720e:


    pl "...We shouldn't let anyone in on our relationship.{w} If bad rumors spread, you'll be the one in trouble."


translate English day9_cr_d1c90620:


    pl "I totally understand how you're feeling, but we should both keep quiet about it for our sakes."


translate English day9_cr_c7de6991:


    cr "I thought you'd say that..."


translate English day9_cr_f66a2a6a:


    pl "...Do you want everyone to know?"


translate English day9_cr_bdb1bbc6:


    cr "If I'm being perfectly honest, yes.{w} I just feel like it's such a waste not to..."


translate English day9_cr_6f99c5b7:


    cr "But I understand your viewpoint.{w} I shan't make such a mistake again."


translate English day9_cr_d7287233:


    pl "Also, this is a good chance to tell you that I'm not really on good terms with the Cleanup Department."


translate English day9_cr_76e8f3d6:


    pl "With the whole Magic Department thing, I'm not used to certain parts, and my personality...{w} Well, anyway, they really don't like me much."


translate English day9_cr_182188b6:


    pl "If anything happened, they'd all turn on me."


translate English day9_cr_1304b74e:


    cr "Oh! I hadn't realized...{w} As far as I've seen, though, the Cleanup Department's priests are generally good people."


translate English day9_cr_84a05a7d:


    cr "They always treat me with kindness, at least."


translate English day9_cr_c02be514:


    pl "That's because you're an outsi--{w}er, a guest, so they don't go all out when you're around. Just be careful, okay?"


translate English day9_cr_f3985b14:


    cr "Hmm... I suppose I understand."


translate English day9_cr_d56eaee0:


    pl "...Anything on your mind?"


translate English day9_cr_12ea51bb:


    cr "Me? Well, now, let's see..."


translate English day9_cr_43c1b825:


    cr "Ah, yes! It's not that important, but there's something I wanted to discuss with you."


translate English day9_cr_8915e91e:


    nar "Claire lowers her voice, despite knowing nobody's around."


translate English day9_cr_649cb16d:


    cr "It's about Maya."


translate English day9_cr_14392955:


    pl "What about her?{w} Are you talking about how she was acting?"


translate English day9_cr_45f69242:


    cr "No, it isn't that...{w} Well, I can't say it's wholly unrelated, but..."


translate English day9_cr_6d31ce07:


    cr "Maya seems to be constantly avoiding me lately."


translate English day9_cr_bc92fc99:


    pl "Really? Like how?"


translate English day9_cr_b67e70f6:


    cr "Like... She'll immediately end any conversation I start with her."


translate English day9_cr_c82c8f11:


    cr "I know she's never been much for talking, but lately she hasn't even been responding to me.{w} I'm not sure how to feel about it."


translate English day9_cr_aeee2280:


    pl "Maya's always been like that...{w} Actually, if she's not responding at all, maybe not.{w} But weren't you two together all the time?"


translate English day9_cr_4278b1da:


    pl "Wasn't she just talking to you over the phone yesterday?"


translate English day9_cr_b5166848:


    cr "Yes, and it surprised me as well!{w} She hasn't called much recently. Not for four days prior to that, at least."


translate English day9_cr_58040c52:


    cr "But suddenly she called me yesterday and asked after my health.{w} I was really happy! But..."


translate English day9_cr_aaafcbc2:


    pl "But?"


translate English day9_cr_11e23d8e:


    cr "Well, I'm not sure how to explain this.{w} After I told Maya I was doing well..."


translate English day9_cr_2d53ab79:


    cr "She asked me a lot of questions.{w} About you, in fact."


translate English day9_cr_2358421c:


    cr "Like whether I'd given you my phone number, or whether you'd already called me."


translate English day9_cr_a1d4de8d:


    cr "Or if you knew I was doing well... Things like that."


translate English day9_cr_0d986f60:


    pl "What? Why would she be asking you that stuff?"


translate English day9_cr_5bd32597:


    cr "I'm not sure--that's why I'm talking to you about it!{w} But if I had to guess..."


translate English day9_cr_e629cee8:


    cr "And I hate to talk behind her back like this, but I don't think she likes the fact that you and I have grown closer."


translate English day9_cr_3ecab263:


    cr "In fact, she may outright hate it."


translate English day9_cr_66842f28:


    pl "It seemed like you two were talking just this morning...{w} What were you talking about before I came?"


translate English day9_cr_9c4d10d8:


    cr "Oh, yes. She asked me if anything was troubling me lately."


translate English day9_cr_0052317e:


    cr "I told her no, so we didn't end up talking about very much."


translate English day9_cr_e44e507d:


    cr "But before all that happened, she told me to be careful."


translate English day9_cr_b89b8595:


    pl "Then summing up...{w} Maya's already caught onto us being together, and wants us to break up."


translate English day9_cr_06a4d7c2:


    cr "I'm sorry?{w} I think it's still to early to assume she wants us to break up."


translate English day9_cr_63606687:


    pl "Hey, I don't want to think it either, but we can't explain her behavior otherwise."


translate English day9_cr_f4360b74:


    pl "She's always been so weak-willed, but she was practically yelling."


translate English day9_cr_b858321c:


    cr "Still... She's the one other person I never want to lie to."


translate English day9_cr_530f5b18:


    pl "I don't think we'd be able to fool her in the first place."


translate English day9_cr_c0e7ec3f:


    nar "Maya knowing about everything isn't surprising--what's surprising is how she directly intervened in something."


translate English day9_cr_646969a2:


    nar "Until now, she's watched my sins from afar, occasionally giving a gentle word of caution, then disappearing."


translate English day9_cr_2337562a:


    nar "I never imagined she'd ever be that assertive."


translate English day9_cr_85a9e1f3:


    nar "And if she did so to prevent another sin... Then what sin could that possibly be?"


translate English day9_cr_b8335e20:


    pl "If Maya's sure of our relationship and seriously pushes us to break up, what would you do?"


translate English day9_cr_eb65d57e:


    cr "As I said before, I would not be able to lie to her."


translate English day9_cr_fa92a914:


    cr "I would make our positions very clear. If she doesn't understand or accept it even then..."


translate English day9_cr_6c4eac12:


    cr "I hate to think about the possibility, but I would have no choice but to stop being friends with her."


translate English day9_cr_8bc90256:


    pl "Romance over friendship, then..."


translate English day9_cr_db7539bb:


    nar "Well, that should have been obvious in this situation.{w} Claire is propping herself up by being dependent on me."


translate English day9_cr_e363ca84:


    nar "Making a choice to avoid a terrible situation, only for that choice to create a new one--what a joke."


translate English day9_cr_13852643:


    pl "Anything else on your mind?"


translate English day9_cr_a2ac35fc:


    cr "On my mind... Yes, there is.{w} It's somewhat embarrassing, but it's something I've been thinking about."


translate English day9_cr_a652a9fb:


    cr "Lord [na], what is your relationship with Lady Arne Alternata?"


translate English day9_cr_3010dced:


    pl "What, with Arnie?"


translate English day9_cr_0bc85567:


    cr "Oh? \"Arnie\"?{w} Are we talking about the same person?"


translate English day9_cr_55b5a2e2:


    pl "She said it was okay. Actually, I haven't seen her recently...{w} Does the whole engagement thing bother you?"


translate English day9_cr_0c7cbc9d:


    cr "Of course it does. Why wouldn't it?!"


translate English day9_cr_eac02aff:


    cr "If you wish to continue building a relationship with me, you should settle your relationship with her as well."


translate English day9_cr_ef84fd4e:


    pl "I mean... It's not something to \"settle,\" here.{w} She's really just a slightly older girl I happen to know."


translate English day9_cr_0ae0e6a9:


    pl "I don't think it's anything to get worked up over.{w} And the issue isn't just a relationship one--my department transfer is riding on it."


translate English day9_cr_025a8ab2:


    cr "That transfer isn't something to worry about in any case.{w} Once you and I are married, you'll have to leave the temple."


translate English day9_cr_e3f487ca:


    cr "I'm not asking you to do it this instant, of course.{w} It's just been on my mind, is all."


translate English day9_cr_373f9412:


    nar "I've been thinking this for a while about Claire..."


translate English day9_cr_cb6bd567:


    pl "I'm not trying to hurt you by saying this, it's just something bothering me...{w} I'm really not as cool a person as you think I am."


translate English day9_cr_3081febe:


    cr "Oh, you are so overly self-conscious!"


translate English day9_cr_7125f006:


    pl "What I mean is, whatever you're hoping for, it's not gonna be easy for me to live up to it."


translate English day9_cr_f005d42a:


    pl "I don't think I'm like most other people.{w} And not like I'm special or anything, just..."


translate English day9_cr_5a618e9d:


    pl "It's hard for me to endure certain things that normal people would find easy."


translate English day9_cr_5e232bce:


    cr "Hmm..."


translate English day9_cr_bd5648bc:


    pl "...Does that make any sense?"


translate English day9_cr_671a5c1d:


    cr "You mean to say that what the average person does normally causes you distress, yes?"


translate English day9_cr_1757234d:


    cr "But that might be your overactive self-consciousness, you know--a misunderstanding, so to speak."


translate English day9_cr_167b1e3d:


    cr "Everyone's scared of doing things they're not accustomed to, right?"


translate English day9_cr_163ae562:


    cr "I don't think it means you're somehow lower than average.{w} It's just that you're a normal person who doesn't know himself very well yet."


translate English day9_cr_4326b301:


    pl "That's possible, but I do seem to struggle an awful lot with certain things..."


translate English day9_cr_8d339f8c:


    cr "Well, whatever they are, staying locked up in the temple will only narrow your perspective."


translate English day9_cr_d671e48e:


    cr "You might be surprised--a little while in the outside air, and your problems might fly away!{w} Or it'll at least give you a break from them."


translate English day9_cr_584aa97e:


    nar "Thoughts and feelings really are tough to get across, huh?"


translate English day9_cr_f181d979:


    nar "Or maybe, like I did before, she's realized it, but is still pretending she hasn't."


translate English day9_cr_ae8873f0:


    nar "As always, she believes I'm special.{w} I want to tell her that she knows nothing."


translate English day9_cr_d9802c53:


    nar "That my sins won't just go away if I avert my eyes from reality."


translate English day9_cr_9b89b1e3:


    nar "That I bear the burden of sins I've accumulated by tempting naive girls like her."


translate English day9_cr_1ecf6654:


    nar "Everything that's happened, past and future, down to the most minute events, will be my burden to bear."


translate English day9_cr_0cf63ca3:


    nar "She is without sin, and I envy her for that..."


translate English day9_cr_88bd086f:


    cr "In any event, would you like to go on a date?{w} We can say you're escorting the good Lady Myosotis."


translate English day9_cr_4c332fda:


    cr "I'll assume all the responsibility for it."


translate English day9_cr_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_cr_e0d29fd5:


    nar "I almost did it again--criticize her.{w} She's already suffering, and I'm doing this instead of trying to help? I'm pathetic."


translate English day9_cr_c148077f:


    nar "I know that no matter how hard this is for me, it's way harder for her!" with sshake


translate English day9_cr_8a95a5b3:


    nar "Claire is still engaged in dangerous stuff, and I decided I'd be at her side anyway."


translate English day9_cr_51f326bd:


    nar "It's only natural I bear the responsibility.{w} And here I am, feeling like it's so rough for me because of something so dumb."


translate English day9_cr_8f0ec90b:


    cr "Is that not okay...?"


translate English day9_cr_fa03d01a:


    pl "N-No, no. It's very thoughtful of you.{w} If that's what you want to do, that's what we'll do."


translate English day9_cr_2cf17eeb:


    cr "Ahaha! You're so silly.{w} But I'm happy. Nobody will have any idea what we're doing."


translate English day9_cr_90b10a28:


    cr "We'll be free.{w} We'll create lots of secrets between us and build our relationship into something irreplaceable for both of us."


translate English day9_cr_ff8e3d54:


    nar "Claire starts to laugh again.{w} Even with her words suffocating me, I have to make the choice. I have to steel myself."


translate English day9_cr_c9340220:



    nvl clear
    "\n Claire tugs on my arm as the town flies by at a dizzying pace, my all-black habit the only thing that doesn't fit the scenery."


translate English day9_cr_639b5816:


    "It feels kind of strange to be walking around town without a single cleaning implement on me. If I wasn't arm in arm with her, I probably wouldn't have had a clue what to do with my hands."


translate English day9_cr_e62ae363:


    et "Compared to me, Claire--freed from the temple's dismal shadows, now running through the streets--looks as though she'd regained her former light. The sight of her reminds me suddenly of the dream I had this morning."


translate English day9_cr_2a375674:



    nvl clear
    "\n But one thing is different--I'm not having much fun. Still, I do my best to respond to the conversations she starts.{w} I can't focus on any of them, but I'm so scared of topics running dry that we end up talking about movies I've never had much interest in."


translate English day9_cr_b37394f4:


    et "And then, at last, the conversation ends. Claire suggests we sit down for a rest, almost as though she's been waiting for this moment."


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_cbfb6c8a:


    "\n We rent a room in an inn--a far cry from an expensive hotel.{w} It's so old the sign out front is fading.{w} A lot of young couples without much money--plus a few unbecoming adults--visit it frequently."


translate English day9_cr_1b853ebb:


    et "The man at the desk who takes the money from Claire gives us a look, but doesn't say anything. He's probably used to people like us--people wearing priest's robes--visiting this place.{w} That just makes me feel even worse."


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_23b0f14c:


    "\n \"Is it your first time being to a place like this?\" asks Claire casually before we enter the room."


translate English day9_cr_b5ec23ef:


    et "I should respond by asking her the same question back, {w}but I ignore her instead, not wanting to know the answer."


translate English day9_cr_cd40919d:



    nvl clear
    "\n Claire giggles to herself as she jumps onto the bed that takes up most of the tiny room.{w} The lights are off but the afternoon sun shines through a gap in her thin curtains, making everything hazy."


translate English day9_cr_9090278c:


    "The murky light illuminates her smile. {w}It's like she's expecting me to straddle her, run my fingers through her fine hair, and shower her sweaty forehead, neck, and eyelids with kisses."


translate English day9_cr_cc45d9a3:


    "Which is exactly what I do. I can feel her warm breath and her pounding heartbeat."


translate English day9_cr_d8bfe481:


    et "I'm still not good at this but as long as I remember the right order, I can finish without difficulty. {w}All I have to do is attend to her for an hour or a half."


translate English day9_cr_de40263e:



    nvl clear
    "\n Which is why I wasn't expecting her to break the silence and initiate conversation."


translate English day9_cr_e284dc3c:


    "\"You won't do anything to me, will you, Lord [na]?\""


translate English day9_cr_9879e5d4:


    extend " she says with her face buried in the sheets, her voice crisp and clear. She sounds out of breath."


translate English day9_cr_9dd1d8f1:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I'm doing it right now.\""


translate English day9_cr_c153fd28:


    "\"I didn't mean like that..."


translate English day9_cr_9049121a:


    et "I meant more like, you won't strangle me or punch me in the stomach, right?\""


translate English day9_cr_86c6d4a9:



    nvl clear
    "\n Of course not. Thinking she's telling some dark joke, all I can do in response to such a seemingly absurd question is to laugh. {w}It's an exasperated snicker."


translate English day9_cr_acad7d79:


    et "She laughs along with me but I can tell she meant it seriously from the way the blood slowly drains from her face."


translate English day9_cr_dd937a8e:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"What's wrong? This is what you want, right?\""


translate English day9_cr_4a95de5d:


    "\"I guess that's one way to look at it...\""


translate English day9_cr_b2aa584f:


    "She blushes, fidgeting as much as when she confessed her embarrassing kink. {w}I stare at the bruises covering her body in horror."


translate English day9_cr_42238b90:


    "She's had a lot of bad experiences with men over the years, to the point where she had no choice but to be satisfied with her unfortunate lot in life."


translate English day9_cr_53786a71:


    et "Which is probably what led to her bizarre sexual appetite. An appetite that had grown deep roots."


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_a7c44437:


    "\n \"But it just doesn't make sense. How can we feel good if it doesn't hurt?\""


translate English day9_cr_fb6c6f9b:


    et "Our conversation doesn't go any further. The discomfort of the past which had almost disappeared completely comes creeping back. The sticky liquid flowing down my throat, glisteningly dirty flesh, the sickening images passing through my head."


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_eeabc09c:


    "\n I shove her bruise-covered body down, trying to shake it all off. I can feel her hard bones and her organs underneath my fingertips. {w}What the hell is wrong with me?"


translate English day9_cr_aa8358b2:


    "Not wanting to think about it anymore, I wrap my hands around her neck. {w}Her neck, so slender I could easily grip it in one hand, stops moving."


translate English day9_cr_cd0fab72:


    et "Unable to exhale, all she can do is inhale repeatedly. Her labored breathing makes me feel like I'm suffocating as well. I can't tell if the sweat in my palms is mine or Claire's."


translate English day9_cr_f13b70b0:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Kiss me. Right now...{w} Lord [na]!\""


translate English day9_cr_5324bdea:


    et "She manages to get out before I cut off her air flow completely. Her hurried plea wasn't for me to stop, but to keep going."


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_58d9a719:


    "\nFinding myself in a desperate situation, I have no choice but to spread her slender legs. Her lips move, as if urging me on."


translate English day9_cr_b9dac9b4:


    "I punch her in the face with my free hand in an attempt at shutting her up."


translate English day9_cr_d8c9d0f7:


    "My hand aches from the hard bones in her face. She trembles. {w}Her pupils are wide, dilated by excitement and fear. Her heart's beating so hard, it feels like it might burst."


translate English day9_cr_29e93ad7:



    nvl clear
    "\nWhile my body is hot, my head gets progressively cooler. It's strange how my hands feel stronger. My breathing gets heavier as hers gets fainter."


translate English day9_cr_fbd21368:


    et "I'm taking such deep breaths and yet I feel dizzy, as if my brain is being deprived of oxygen. My hands are slipping from a mixture of tears and sweat. {w}Claire looks like she's about to scream."


translate English day9_cr_bcd000f6:



    nvl clear
    "\nOf course, she can't make any sound at all with my hands around her neck. I don't want to hear her voice again. Hearing her innocent voice is too painful."


translate English day9_cr_caae34a1:


    et "Instead of those lost memories, I try to imagine the pain she's feeling. {w}As I look down at the scar that's become more pronounced, thanks to me, I feel that moment when her memories of past violence is obscurred by me."


translate English day9_cr_17b3e982:



    nvl clear
    "\nHer tongue moves, as if I'm violating her mind. Her body spasms, as if she's having a seizure. Eventually, her tongue falls still, her body spent."


translate English day9_cr_479a6227:


    "She's beyond pale to purple, like a corpse. Her tongue, pointed like a dagger, hovers motionless in the air. I can hear my voice as I struggle to breathe and realize I started screaming at some point."


translate English day9_cr_1d2e4328:


    "Cold air seeps into my brain."


translate English day9_cr_03f404ce:


    "What the hell did I do? What's wrong with me?"


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_9:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_3b1da0b3:


    "\n \"Urk!\"" with sshake


translate English day9_cr_79bc10e1:


    "Which is the exact moment when I wake up. {w}It's also the moment when all the gastric juices that had been collecting in the pit of my stomach come rushing back up my esophagus."


translate English day9_cr_92524423:


    et "At the same time, I begin sobbing, tears pouring down my face."


translate English day9_cr_22a69951:



    nvl clear
    "\nThe sound of me puking mixes with Claire's hacking coughs. {w}She's probably experiencing the same acidic smell and taste spreading from my nose."


translate English day9_cr_c72176cc:


    et "In the end, however, Claire stops coughing first."


translate English day9_cr_fec7f77d:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I'm...I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.\""


translate English day9_cr_0da2abf6:


    et "I wanted to give her an actual apology but my clogged nose makes it difficult to talk. Claire is alive. {w}Not only that, but she looks more confused than me."


translate English day9_cr_1528c0c9:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I-I'm the one who feels bad. You must've been more exhausted from work than I realized, and I pushed you too far... {w}Well, what now?\""


translate English day9_cr_8ff90fe5:


    "She gently rubs my back before taking me to the bathroom."


translate English day9_cr_03d0c995:


    "The feeling of nausea had passed and my breathing had returned to normal but I still couldn't look her in the eyes. {w}The air in the bathroom felt cool but I couldn't stop trembling because of another reason all together."


translate English day9_cr_49b09c91:



    nvl clear
    "\nI want to go back... To be anywhere but here."


translate English day9_cr_10d5a7a9:


    et "I cry, trying to keep my sobs as quiet as possible. {w}I'm shaking so hard that it's clear this isn't some tragic nightmare."


translate English day9_cr_c7f6efe0:


    nar "When I come back out, Claire is cleaning up the vomit on the floor."


translate English day9_cr_fe1fcc6b:


    nar "If her goal is to make me feel miserable, then she's a genius."


translate English day9_cr_9b984a73:


    nar "After that, we get back into her spacious bed, simply lying side by side."


translate English day9_cr_4104ae30:


    nar "The unfamiliar lighting and faint smell of wood makes me drowsy."


translate English day9_cr_c7037497:


    cr "I'm sorry. This is all my fault... I'm sure you've had a better time with other women."


translate English day9_cr_d1f16daa:


    pl "No... I'm just drained from work."


translate English day9_cr_f83e1f28:


    nar "I answer without looking at her. She gazes up at the ceiling, just like me."


translate English day9_cr_eef5da0f:


    pl "Hey, why'd you end up having to get married to a guy like that?"


translate English day9_cr_e25271e6:


    pl "Your family has money...{w} And you said you wanted to work at the temple, didn't you?"


translate English day9_cr_622a3b5f:


    cr "Hmm. You want to know the why...{w} I was the one who accepted the marriage. I've always wanted to be a bride."


translate English day9_cr_98110512:


    cr "I went to the temple because I wanted to have experiences I wouldn't be able to after getting married, then took a bit of a shine to the work there."


translate English day9_cr_b7ec68d5:


    cr "My family may have money, but it's not endless.{w} Marrying someone with even more would help my parents a lot, too."


translate English day9_cr_0f0065f5:


    pl "So it was on a whim."


translate English day9_cr_a48eef91:


    cr "Oh, another thing. Unrelated to how you meant your question, but...{w} People whose stigmata appear in strange places are valued for their rarity."


translate English day9_cr_b58031bf:


    cr "I've been pulled every which way constantly for it.{w} Look at me. It's in my eye, right?"


translate English day9_cr_e1032a5a:


    cr "That makes it very unusual!"


translate English day9_cr_deafe828:


    pl "What's so good about it? You're a person, not an object.{w} That stupid stigmata makes it hard for you to see, doesn't it?"


translate English day9_cr_9e7324b9:


    pl "That's not value. That's a disability that needs to be cared for.{w} The only ones who would assign value to that are the maniacs who treat people like slaves."


translate English day9_cr_eb216167:


    cr "Hmm?"


translate English day9_cr_0fbbe92c:


    pl "Anyway, people here are weird.{w} They discriminate based on hair color, look down on others for their number of stigmata..."


translate English day9_cr_3cd030c1:


    pl "Where I lived, at least, everyone's a friend.{w} I have these weird arm scars, right?"


translate English day9_cr_04d3e965:


    pl "I can't work properly, my pronunciation is all weird, and I've got no parents... But nobody discriminated against me."


translate English day9_cr_d05382d0:


    cr "Really... The people in your homeland must all be rich in spirit, Lord [na]."


translate English day9_cr_e7bb8399:


    pl "Rich in spirit? You've completely got it backwards. Their views are so narrow they can't see anything else."


translate English day9_cr_7ba8e091:


    cr "Did your parents... pass very soon after your birth?"


translate English day9_cr_886086d0:


    pl "Nah. They both lived in the village. But for a really long time, I thought they weren't my birth parents."


translate English day9_cr_ec3c04cd:


    pl "Sometimes the adults would look at me and talk about my mother, but it was like it never had anything to do with me."


translate English day9_cr_47ef9635:


    pl "I wish I'd just stayed ignorant about it."


translate English day9_cr_56da6e20:


    cr "Then you've met them?"


translate English day9_cr_4469be0c:


    pl "I went to see them, but that's it.{w} When I saw how happily my mother was living, I..."


translate English day9_cr_39be3f34:


    pl "I realized I would just get in the way of my her life.{w} So, like. I've always been an orphan. Honest."


translate English day9_cr_b6fe7b07:


    cr "I see... But it seems like your family was very free, Lord [na].{w} More free than the temple is, at least."


translate English day9_cr_2737e78b:


    cr "Earrings are forbidden at the temple too, you know. Did you do the piercing yourself?"


translate English day9_cr_cb623d1d:


    pl "Well... Yeah, I guess."


translate English day9_cr_a3e96422:


    cr "Oh! Then would you do the same for my ears?"


translate English day9_cr_d4b71920:


    pl "I mean, I guess I don't mind. But why?"


translate English day9_cr_9332ae71:


    cr "Well, I can't work at the temple anymore anyway.{w} It's natural I'd want to do at least that much. And..."


translate English day9_cr_a6837c16:


    cr "I feel as though each time I look at a wound from you, Lord [na], it would set my heart at ease."


translate English day9_cr_eb1e660c_3:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_10:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_2d428ae4:


    nar "I take out my left earring and wipe it on the blanket, then gently grasp her ear."


translate English day9_cr_270bdc9d:


    nar "It's my first time touching it, of course, but also my first time seeing it up close like this."


translate English day9_cr_e8515733:


    nar "I do my best not to let my hand shake, but that seems to have the opposite effect."


translate English day9_cr_3237efa9:


    nar "Claire's slender ears easily accept the pin, though, without hesitation."


translate English day9_cr_3f6f6cc0:


    nar "Her white ear swells with red, but she doesn't even yelp.{w} She must sincerely feel happy about the pain."


translate English day9_cr_718466f2:


    cr "Well, I saw my parents yesterday."


translate English day9_cr_53e4ab28:


    nar "Her face still happy, she continues the conversation."


translate English day9_cr_0ef0dd75:


    cr "I understand that they both love me, but sometimes I get the feeling they don't understand me."


translate English day9_cr_059fe369:


    cr "They'd do anything for me, and it scares me to think I might never leave the nest."


translate English day9_cr_4925f01b:


    cr "If they found me doing this sort of thing with you, they would be very sad indeed."


translate English day9_cr_3bfcbc32:


    cr "But they'd never disown me, certainly!"


translate English day9_cr_99c548c2:


    nar "Still tidying up her fine hair, she speaks of the love she receives, the privilege she enjoys."


translate English day9_cr_09626a5d:


    nar "She speaks of her happiness--all without seeming to realize it."


translate English day9_cr_eb1e660c_4:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_cr_7b4fee35:


    cr "I believe that's why you attracted me, Lord [na].{w} I long for a life of freedom, without an ounce of pressure."


translate English day9_cr_80ca1d87:


    cr "And yet each time I feel a wall between me and my beloved, it saddens me."


translate English day9_cr_943b75f5:


    cr "I learned that after meeting you."


translate English day9_cr_eb1e660c_5:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_cr_ad6c44f7:


    cr "Nobody actually loves me.{w} Even Maya has come to hate me."


translate English day9_cr_eb1e660c_6:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_cr_e8e51f61:


    cr "I must truly be a poor unfortunate soul."


translate English day9_cr_c293d743:


    nar "The earring sparkles in her ear, as though not fully grasping what's in her heart."


translate English day9_cr_1a36def3:


    nar "In the dim room, that glow seems to be reflecting the light from Claire herself."


translate English day9_cr_d90ad801:


    nar "Maya suddenly leaps to mind, and I really start hating myself for it."


translate English day9_cr_7c9c9ef6:


    nar "We talked after that, and I gave her kiss near the lips, but I don't really remember."


translate English day9_cr_d32d5675:


    nar "Now that I think of it, I have to return that book to the library soon.{w} What did I borrow again...? Was it the infirmary that borrowed something?"


translate English day9_cr_007603a0:


    nar "At some point, I realize Claire is dozing.{w} Noticing her lack of a response, I belatedly feel the exhaustion."


translate English day9_cr_c5ef9a99:


    nar "What to do now..."


translate English day9_cr_f0e6ad40:


    pl "...?!" with sshake


translate English day9_cr_4e253635:


    nar "Did I accidentally fall asleep?{w} What time is it? I hurry to pat down my hair and pull on my clothes."


translate English day9_cr_52fc8f9f:


    nar "I'd hoped it wasn't night out, but the clock's already gone past that--it says it's three in the morning."


translate English day9_cr_9dd10ec0:


    nar "I burst outside without any real plan, but the scenery of the village--quiet, nobody walking around under the white sky--says it all."


translate English day9_cr_b32b401f:


    nar "I'm terrified--panicking. I can't think."


translate English day9_cr_44f5a5de:


    nar "But in my mind, I'm terribly calm. My weak legs tremble, though, as if they're the only thing that understands this situation."


translate English day9_cr_7ffc93da:


    cr "Lord [na]!" with sshake


translate English day9_cr_fa5a7e51:


    nar "A few moments later, Claire follows me out. She catches her breath."


translate English day9_cr_5d6a1a8c:


    cr "What's going on?{w} You, you suddenly ran outside..."


translate English day9_cr_adcaced5:


    pl "I dozed off and lost track of the time...{w} We left the temple too quickly to put in a request."


translate English day9_cr_f28dde0c:


    pl "And we didn't talk about it to anyone else... The dorm has a curfew, so I wouldn't be able to get in if I went back... And how long would it even take to get there if I walked?"


translate English day9_cr_bf75814f:


    pl "Right. How are you getting home?{w} Taking a cab, I guess? I'm seriously sorry. I should have been more aware..."


translate English day9_cr_e55e8418:


    cr "No, it's... I'm..."


translate English day9_cr_435b32d8:


    cr "Sigh. I'll take a late night train by myself. I think they still run at this hour."


translate English day9_cr_d639ce00:


    cr "And I happen to know the way there, so... It should be fine."


translate English day9_cr_616f246a:


    pl "Right... So you're going, then? I'm sorry..."


translate English day9_cr_feccdeae:


    cr "The earlier you get back, the better, I'm sure.{w} Please take care as you go, Lord [na]."


translate English day9_cr_03a62c54:


    pl "Y-Yeah. You be careful too. I'll see you tomorrow...{w} And, uh... I'd prefer it if you pretended that none of this ever happened."


translate English day9_cr_8c5c0316:


    cr "Huh? You mean what happened today?{w} Pretending it didn't... That's..."


translate English day9_cr_ad78fc57:


    cr "Alright, I understand. Let's just get home for now.{w} Or else we'll end up being even later."


translate English day9_cr_740dc951:


    pl "Right, yeah... I'm really sorry about this."


translate English day9_cr_0b6db0d4:


    nar "I run off in the other direction.{w} I hear cats in heat meowing, their cries like little children; the capital must have its fair share of strays."


translate English day9_cr_13ac2762:


    nar "If I'd had the time to, I would have turned back for a moment, but I'm in such a hurry that I don't give Claire a good look."


translate English day9_cr_874a3a5d:


    nar "I hope she got home alright.{w} How can I be running this irresponsibly? I know exactly what her position is."


translate English day9_cr_e810c6dd:


    nar "There's nothing I can do about it, though, and the temple is already in sight."


translate English day9_cr_7f6d7867:


    nar "I made it through the checkpoint somehow, but the dorm is, as expected, locked up.{w} I take a look around."


translate English day9_cr_8f78d2fc:


    nar "But nobody else would be hanging around outside the dorm at this hour.{w} The sun rises as if to taunt me."


translate English day9_cr_cc630975:


    nar "And today, I hate that sun so much more.{w} My legs are heavy from all the running. I basically can't even see at this point--I haven't for a while."


translate English day9_cr_aaf13a73:


    nar "My head grows dull. I'll just find a bush somewhere and..."


translate English day9_cr_08f27291:


    sc "Who's there?"


translate English day9_cr_e703a784:


    pl "Geh!" with sshake


translate English day9_cr_367334d9:


    sc "...[na]?{w} Is that you?"


translate English day9_cr_1a4abab4:


    pl "Securett..."


translate English day9_cr_be222b53:


    sc "What on earth are you doing out this late?{w} Do you have any idea how much trouble you've caused?!"


translate English day9_cr_3e63538f:


    sc "I wish you would have at least told me first!{w} I thought you'd gotten used to being here. I swear..." with sshake


translate English day9_cr_74378ced:


    pl "Hey... Wait, just hold on!{w} I know it caused a lot of trouble, but hear me out first! I didn't have a choice." with sshake


translate English day9_cr_525b240e:


    pl "I didn't want to be out all day without telling anyone either!{w} It was an accident!"


translate English day9_cr_7af6fb13:


    sc "What...?"


translate English day9_cr_6ab6e993:


    pl "Well... Claire came this morning, and she said we should go out.{w} I didn't see any way to turn her down, so..."


translate English day9_cr_77791284:


    sc "......"


translate English day9_cr_21706529:


    sc "...I see."


translate English day9_cr_0a46dc32:


    nar "......?"


translate English day9_cr_ca4f0b5c:


    sc "Alright. You look pretty tired. Get back inside and get some sleep."


translate English day9_cr_1531926b:


    pl "W-Wait, what?"


translate English day9_cr_955bb51d:


    sc "I work late a lot, so I have a spare key.{w} Good thing you ran into me before hiding in the bushes, huh?"


translate English day9_cr_96f204e0:


    nar "Despite all that anger, Securett now calmly unlocks the door."


translate English day9_cr_710ea2cc:


    nar "On top of that, he opens it for me, trying to let me in first.{w} I've never felt quite so lucky."


translate English day9_cr_b216d7d5:


    nar "Because I AM lucky he was here. Lucky--and that's all.{w} I walk past him before he changes his mind."


translate English day9_cr_a3c1b93e:


    sc "...Your hair's wet."


translate English day9_cr_df74665a:


    nar "Or at least, I would have, but those words made reality come crashing down me again.{w} Something like this has happened before."


translate English day9_cr_47da47d1:


    nar "I've forgotten the words I heard then, but I very much remember the terror I felt."


translate English day9_cr_14d222e0:


    nar "I leave, fleeing into the dark hallway. Naturally, he doesn't follow me.{w} I'm alone in my fear."


translate English day9_cr_d35bbafe:


    nar "Should I really be anywhere near her?{w} Should I really stay the way I am?"


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_11:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_12:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_cr_b2b0e5dd:


    et "\n \"No. No, of course I shouldn't.\""


translate English day9_cr_ef8b9edb:



    nvl clear
    "\n I kneel before the angel's room.{w} All the earnest priests are fast asleep; the dorm is unusually quiet."


translate English day9_cr_7844a6dc:


    et "A sinner's voice will reach her more clearly."


translate English day9_cr_2abe72ac:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I just wanted her to live a better life.{w} I just wanted her to be somewhere safer, somewhere secure.{w} But the longer we're together, the worse things get.{w} I've tried to help where I can, but I don't think this is good.\""


translate English day9_cr_c18b1ded:


    et "I can sense the angel's presence beyond the thin door.{w} I had intended to confess my sins alone, but what spills from my mouth now are only complaints.{w} But the angel listens in silence, letting me speak freely."


translate English day9_cr_906905a3:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Every time I do anything, it hurts her.{w} I know exactly how much she's suffering, and I can't do a thing about it. All I can do is listen!"


translate English day9_cr_627d4ff9:


    "Sometimes, I wonder what it would be like if she'd looked for help from someone else.{w} If she had someone else to save her, if there had been a different path for us...\""


translate English day9_cr_9f9c498c:


    "The sins flowing from my mouth are hot, and they catch in my throat.{w} But I shed no tears. It's not time for tears yet.{w} I still cannot let this relationship end."


translate English day9_cr_e60bb433:


    et "The angel gives me no answers, but I can sense a comforting warmth from the other side of the door."


translate English day9_cr_76b2fe88_13:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_cr_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_cr_143f56ed:


    nar "I head to my room, same as always."


translate English day10_cr_5aaed44a:


    nar "As the air begins to feel even colder on my body, I hear someone talking in the distance."


translate English day10_cr_f89af91f:


    nar "But this hallway is quiet. Not a single soul in sight."


translate English day10_cr_83bd8d5c:


    nar "I calmly try to open my door, but the hand I use feels so heavy.{w} It's not locked. I still can't sense anyone around."


translate English day10_cr_abe41a7e:


    nar "But I know someone is on the other side. Rallying my strength, I open the firmly closed door."


translate English day10_cr_db2781ff:


    nar "And there I see light.{w} Wind blows in from the thrown-open window, and I shut my eyes before the radiant, white room."


translate English day10_cr_1ed22116:


    nar "Because of how intense the light is, when I next open my eyes, I feel slightly dizzy."


translate English day10_cr_3eaa6651:


    nar "A girl, fair-skinned and naked, stands bathing in the light, her back to me."


translate English day10_cr_159d46d1:


    nar "It is the huge wings growing from her spine and shoulder blades creating and scattering the light."


translate English day10_cr_10a5fa6b:


    nar "I want to go closer and nestle up to her, but my feet feel as though they're rooted to the ground."


translate English day10_cr_6c158c2f:


    nar "With me unable to move, she slowly turns around and approaches me.{w} I understand that she's an angel."


translate English day10_cr_e3f7363f:


    nar "I'm not scared. The angel has appeared in the form of a girl I know, and offers me her gentle smile."


translate English day10_cr_4a02ec36:


    nar "That smile soothes my fear and speaks to me.{w} \"Hello,\" it says."


translate English day10_cr_a4f030f0:


    pl "H-He... Hello."


translate English day10_cr_0d8f4d81:


    nar "She blinks in response to my greeting.{w} She looks at me with dilated pupils."


translate English day10_cr_e52bdf20:


    nar "How fortunate must it be to touch an angel? To be able to talk to one?"


translate English day10_cr_a8a79047:


    nar "Not a single lie would pass my lips--I could only speak the truth to her."


translate English day10_cr_3c662cb3:


    pl "I said before there was nothing bothering me...{w} But that was a lie. I'm really sorry."


translate English day10_cr_f18c227a:


    my2 "It's alright."


translate English day10_cr_aba46e06:


    nar "In two words, the angel forgives me. I feel my face heating up."


translate English day10_cr_5ff99a8b:


    pl "It's just...{w} Claire and I are going out right now. And I love her, of course, but it's like..."


translate English day10_cr_5952a874:


    pl "It's like the harder I try, the more complicated it gets."


translate English day10_cr_94a4399c:


    nar "I bow my heavy head, then hear her laughing, the sound tickling my ears.{w} She's looking at me and laughing."


translate English day10_cr_e7440cd2:


    my2 "[na2], you have it all wrong."


translate English day10_cr_b1fa463e:


    pl "I do?"


translate English day10_cr_620bf424:


    my2 "All wrong... Ahaha..."


translate English day10_cr_439c8387:


    pl "Wh-What?{w} What do I have wrong?"


translate English day10_cr_e700eeeb:


    my2 "So silly. So embarrassing!{w} So pitiful, the two of you are..."


translate English day10_cr_e63ceb6d:


    pl "I'm asking what I'm getting wrong here... Please, tell me."


translate English day10_cr_41ab4508:


    pl "Tell me!" with sshake


translate English day10_cr_8edec8e6:



    nvl clear
    et "\n The angel never answers.{w} Before she says anything, my consciousness feels like its fading, fading, fading..."


