translate English day11_cr_497860f8:


    "I figured she'd come to see me right after getting to the temple.{w} Is she worried about being seen with me?"


translate English day11_cr_a8892305:


    et "I leave the folder where it is and immediately run out towards the stairwell.{w} She probably thinks I was waiting there for her."


translate English day11_cr_c85c110c:



    nvl clear
    "\n Unfortunately, though, there's nobody around.{w} I was stupid for believing that rumor."


translate English day11_cr_19771186:


    "The stairwell is quiet, damp, dark, and cold.{w} I feel bad for her--having lost her place, having been driven into a corner, having found only romance and intimacy in this dim space.{w} Did we really have nowhere else to go?"


translate English day11_cr_21131142:


    et "We'd go to other places from now on.{w} Instead of staying cooped up in this dusty old place, we could go to the towns Claire's always excitedly spoken of, or go beyond the sea.{w} Go somewhere nobody else would know. Somewhere we wouldn't have to rely on a god without answers.{w} This time, I won't make the same mistake."


translate English day11_cr_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_cr_6254c85a:


    "\n I hear voices in the distance.{w} But I stay put, waiting for Claire, though I don't know if she's even coming."


translate English day11_cr_e4075e94:


    et "Time passes, and I'd be lying if I said it was any fun.{w} When I see Claire, what should I say to her?{w} I try to imagine her reaction. I remember her voice, what she looks like."


translate English day11_cr_e971f9c3:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Hello there!\""


translate English day11_cr_36616836:


    et "My mind immediately warms with the noise.{w} Her voice is like a cheerful echo, and once I recall it, I can hear more."


translate English day11_cr_d9b2eea3:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I don't have any friends, so... I get very envious watching everyone else at the temple.\""


translate English day11_cr_ef1bd1d6:


    "I didn't want to know about the darkness within her.{w} Not because I wanted to remain ignorant, but because I couldn't help her."


translate English day11_cr_4dfefe6a:


    et "Ever since we first met, I never believed that she would come to me for help.{w} The fact that there was never really anyone to hear her out, the fact that Claire was that lonely--I didn't want to accept that as truth."


translate English day11_cr_56340087:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I've come much too far to change that in the span of a single night.\""


translate English day11_cr_e5986f6f:


    et "She thought I would be able to save her, but that had been youthful ignorance."


translate English day11_cr_a85bd01f:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Because this isn't one of those wait-and-it-goes-away problems.{w} Or were you planning on solving it yourself?\""


translate English day11_cr_e0576187:


    "I knew it all from the start.{w} Claire has always been radiant. Radiant in the same way Maya had described as she'd brushed my hand away."


translate English day11_cr_7d953c0f:


    "It anguished me to see that light marred by unhappiness and misfortune.{w} She'd had the ability to fix her situation. Why hadn't she?{w} Because I hadn't given her the courage to do so?"


translate English day11_cr_77116483:


    et "Where did it all go wrong? What more should I have done?{w} Claire, I just... I just don't get it."


translate English day11_cr_f889d37c:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Nobody will have any idea what we're doing. We'll be free.\""


translate English day11_cr_1592fe5d:


    et "\"We'll create lots of secrets between us and build our relationship into something irreplaceable for both of us.\""


translate English day11_cr_1730141f:



    nvl clear
    et "\n Unless you don't give me a real answer, unless we can't be honest with each other, I'll probably just misunderstand you again."


translate English day11_cr_c862d020:


    cr "...Oh?"


translate English day11_cr_76814ce0:


    nar "I hear a voice alongside graceful steps.{w} I look up and see Claire blinking, staring at me."


translate English day11_cr_65f326cf:


    nar "It's Claire.{w} She's holding her light bag as if she just got to the temple."


translate English day11_cr_5a92577d:


    nar "I've been thinking about her this whole time, but now that we're face to face, I can't speak."


translate English day11_cr_6dee5f8b:


    cr "Lord [na]?{w} It's been a long time since you were here first.{w} Good morning. Are you slacking off again?"


translate English day11_cr_d69ecf34:


    nar "Claire gives a plain smile.{w} My head begins to swim."


translate English day11_cr_501d4dcc:


    nar "Her face looks more grown-up after a day of not seeing her."


translate English day11_cr_6bdd16ae:


    nar "I know everything about her, and she knows about me.{w} But this is as awkward as two people meeting for the first time."


translate English day11_cr_05c3632f:


    nar "Her expression mixes in with all of the childish smiles I remember her giving, and my memories scatter, broken."


translate English day11_cr_8121d2d8:


    nar "Claire is, of course, the one in front of me.{w} She didn't become someone else overnight."


translate English day11_cr_ae5ebdcf:


    nar "Her face one I know very well, she waits for me to respond to her greeting."


translate English day11_cr_671cc268:


    pl "I want you to be happy..."


translate English day11_cr_1e808fdd:


    nar "But the words that come out aren't a greeting.{w} They're not even asking if she's okay."


translate English day11_cr_83474287:


    nar "On these same old stairs, the same old Claire tilts her head, confused at the strange answer.{w} The only thing not \"same old\" is me."


translate English day11_cr_cd876447:


    nar "Ever since getting up this morning--maybe even since last night."


translate English day11_cr_aa3efbe9:


    cr "Yes.{w} I pray for your happiness as well, of course."


translate English day11_cr_36f32274:


    nar "Her answer shakes me.{w} We've talked about our interests and feelings a lot up until now, and it all made sense."


translate English day11_cr_c9bb1015:


    nar "But it didn't lead to us actually understanding each other.{w} Asking each other if we were okay, or being considerate or whatever--that was all just out of a sense of responsibility."


translate English day11_cr_baa86feb:


    nar "If I'd known it was this easy to make myself understood, I would have been more honest a lot sooner."


translate English day11_cr_ea527b79:


    pl "I wanted to make you happy, but I couldn't. I'm sorry.{w} I'm really pathetic."


translate English day11_cr_02b2e796:


    pl "From the start, I've been irresponsible. I've always known I wouldn't be able to help you. I didn't even make the effort to change anything..."


translate English day11_cr_6b761449:


    pl "I was afraid of you loving me, so I hated it when you asked me for help!" with sshake


translate English day11_cr_f09a09fa:


    pl "I've never actually dated anyone, and I'm scared of women...{w} S-So I couldn't be as thoughtful with you as I could have."


translate English day11_cr_8ecc04f6:


    pl "I misunderstood my own feelings.{w} But I'm fine now.{w} At the time, I wasn't sure what to do, I just thought I didn't want it...!" with sshake


translate English day11_cr_1c62d5b9:


    pl "But now I'm grateful... Well... Are we okay now?{w} I should have... have paid a little more attention to your feelings."


translate English day11_cr_8c68e7d2:


    pl "And I will, from now on. Thank you for coming today. Seriously.{w} The only thing left now is to be happy..."


translate English day11_cr_01fb10d4:


    nar "All the words I'd been trying to keep down burst out of me almost at random.{w} Even during them, I thought of Claire's feelings, redoing my sentences several times."


translate English day11_cr_c4cd341b:


    nar "I want to reach out and take her hand, but since I've been staring at the floor this whole time, I only catch air.{w} My fingers tremble in the cold air."


translate English day11_cr_96efd04b:


    cr "Lord [na]..."


translate English day11_cr_968eab29:


    cr "As I'm sure anyone who knows me would say, I'm a delicate romantic."


translate English day11_cr_4a93cafa:


    cr "This utterly unromantic situation, however, is a little troubling for me."


translate English day11_cr_d5de2d97:


    nar "Claire blinks as she answers; the words from her mouth are as strange as my own were."


translate English day11_cr_18feac0b:


    nar "She's not criticizing me--she sounds more like she's criticizing the situation she's in."


translate English day11_cr_85188f7b:


    nar "There's still a smile on her face, but it doesn't seem the same as before.{w} Unlike me, she's staring up at the sky."


translate English day11_cr_4851f3f4:


    cr "To be quiet honest, I don't really understand things."


translate English day11_cr_00f5ed31:


    cr "If you truly are being considerate of my feelings, then shouldn't you be honest in full, such as the case of telling me you hate me?"


translate English day11_cr_fe97af60:


    cr "You only ever think about yourself.{w} You find it annoying to involve yourself with others, and you do nothing but avoid making situations more complicated."


translate English day11_cr_48ab9841:


    cr "And I believe you understand all this, don't you?"


translate English day11_cr_b799518d:


    cr "You're only saying this now that the annoying problem has been solved."


translate English day11_cr_f045f1a5:


    cr "That is something I simply cannot understand."


translate English day11_cr_1de677dc:



    nvl clear
    "\n With slow steps, Claire passes me and climbs up to the balcony.{w} I get a glimpse of her underwear beneath her skirt-- different from usual. But that's normal.{w} And then I realize what was wrong with her smile before."


translate English day11_cr_0348e5a2:


    et "She said it herself--she's mocking me for spewing all these incomprehensible words at her.{w} She's lamenting the situation she's been placed in. She's most *definitely* still mad about yesterday."


translate English day11_cr_0a4e79c8:



    nvl clear
    "\n I don't understand a word she says, either.{w} Whenever Claire expresses her love, she always gives a part of herself.{w} How much can she do for her partner? How much has she given up?"


translate English day11_cr_998fde31:


    et "Women aren't objects; lovers are supposed to be equal in life. But she only ever scorns herself, as though she's disposable.{w} That is probably the standard of Claire's love."


translate English day11_cr_2890df1c:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I love you, Claire.{w} I didn't mean what I said yesterday... I'm sorry.\""


translate English day11_cr_769744e5:


    "So I try to follow her, putting one foot onto the balcony to get closer to her."


translate English day11_cr_fbc7bff0:


    "I've already prepared myself this time to do anything she needs me to, and yet right now, this is the only thing I can do.{w} I creep up on her like she's a wild beast and try not to stimulate her.{w} I don't know why that's the feeling I get, but it is."


translate English day11_cr_311cf5bb:


    et "Because she's closer to a domesticated cat--not an inch of her small body would ever threaten me."


translate English day11_cr_e20bfa3f:



    nvl clear
    "\n With the sun at its apex, white light shines in through the window.{w} Claire brings her face up, but the backlighting prevents me from seeing it very well.{w} The raindrops dripping from the windowsill are like glittering gemstones, actually striking me as a little extravagant."


translate English day11_cr_7e4d0281:


    "I have a feeling I can finally understand why she feels romance from this place."


translate English day11_cr_605f735e:


    et "I squint against the light.{w} Eventually my vision sharpens enough for me to see her face.{w} Once again, I find no despair or anger there.{w} For some reason, that makes me uneasy."


translate English day11_cr_959a88e2:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Claire... I'm sorry.\""


translate English day11_cr_78fbea73:


    "Still afraid, I apologize many times.{w} I've said these words many times today, but they still haven't found her forgiveness."


translate English day11_cr_b2208d06:


    "\"About what?\" she asks.{w} Once again, her question seems to be testing me."


translate English day11_cr_da767831:


    et "If I can't answer properly now, what will become of us?"


translate English day11_cr_6b7a3c5c:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"What are you speaking of, Lord [na]?\""


translate English day11_cr_32cdaf7c:


    "\"E-Everything, all of it...! I'm so sorry.{w} I ignored how sincere you were in liking me... And, well... I'm sorry for getting mad... I love you...!"


translate English day11_cr_b7f9ac50:


    et "We can start over, right?{w} I promise I'll do things right this time...!\""


translate English day11_cr_fa55382d:



    nvl clear
    "\n My mind moves slowly.{w} I tried to decorate my words with ones she likes, but they end up coming out in a mess."


translate English day11_cr_b0f9c9e7:


    et "My legs shake, begging me to run away.{w} For just a moment, I feel like I hear the flapping of angel wings from very close by."


translate English day11_cr_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_cr_1d6d8f14:


    "\n \"It's fine!\""


translate English day11_cr_9663426e:


    "And in that moment, her forgiveness finally comes.{w} She opens her round eyes and smiles."


translate English day11_cr_7075e1cc:


    et "Her immaculate, unclouded smile is the picture of freedom.{w} Drawn by her great, flowing joy, I smile as well."


translate English day11_cr_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_cr_4cc5fcfb:


    cr "I guess we were never actually dating to begin with."


translate English day11_cr_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_cr_2cf6acaa:


    "\n Claire picks up a gun, holds it to her head, and fires.{w} The sequence of actions I see are very clear, but my mind can't process any of them."


translate English day11_cr_20afad45:


    et "The gun is a little big for her tiny hand--her tiny hand that has never known hardship.{w} The gun in question had come from her bag."


translate English day11_cr_c6004c16:



    nvl clear
    "\n When she holds it, even it looks like a toy.{w} What young lady in this world would walk around with a lethal weapon?"


translate English day11_cr_12cdc62f:


    "The actions she takes are so fast and so smooth that my eyes don't keep up.{w} I remember her telling me she'd learn magic that was good enough to shock me. At first, I think that's what's going on."


translate English day11_cr_4d5b2ed0:


    "The barrel never threatens me--it points at Clione."


translate English day11_cr_10aefdd6:


    et "And then she explodes.{w} Her body crumples like a flower scattering its petals, and I hold her in my arms like the ending of a cliche tragedy."


translate English day11_cr_5b88732a:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Ah...\""


translate English day11_cr_bf06b324:


    "Ahhh... ahh... ooh, aaaaahhh, AAAAAAAHHHHHHHHHHHHH!!!{w} A scream escapes me. My vision is red--completely covered with blood." with sshake


translate English day11_cr_dc74e12d:


    "The scattered filth and flesh stick to my face, chunks having made through my hair.{w} They're cold; I shudder."


translate English day11_cr_6f1e8c07:


    "And I shudder so hard that I fall off the balcony and down the stairs, still holding the headless body."


translate English day11_cr_8a051fa6:


    et "My red vision floods with black, and as soon as I open my eyes again, I see lights flashing before me.{w} As I collided, along with the pain all through me, I didn't hear my body collide with anything--instead, I heard a lighter, squishier sound."


translate English day11_cr_82ef5258:



    nvl clear
    "\n The bright light still shines on her.{w} But now, without her head, she is less a \"she\" and more a poorly-constructed mannequin.{w} What little remains of her head hangs down over the gaping hole in her neck."


translate English day11_cr_20432742:


    "Her split head looks yellow, and also blue. Her azure hair that always reminded me of my homeland is dyed in red.{w} Along with blood, a mysterious fluid flows out of her."


translate English day11_cr_13b85da5:


    et "Eyeballs stuck by dark blue threads--and the characteristic stigmata engraved in one of them, expressing its owner.{w} Her peach-colored tongue is briefly visible on her pale face, expressing her existence.{w} Her teeth, small like pure white pebbles on a beach, have flesh stuck to them that looks like cloth."


translate English day11_cr_71fa54dc:



    nvl clear
    "\n Tears, snot, and what looked like cold sweat flows endlessly from the surface of my skin.{w} Nobody is here to speak, so the stairs should be silent--but Claire's bell still rings annoyingly loud in my ears as it moves.{w} I scoop up the thing that helped make her who she was and hold it in my hand."


translate English day11_cr_2acf4965:


    et "The cold floor quickly saps her warmth.{w} The clump in my hands is hard but flexible, like pork."


translate English day11_cr_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_cr_c1b37560:


    "\n When I realize it's her brain, I crawl along the slippery floor and get out to where it's bright."


translate English day11_cr_d840f49c:


    et "What was once Claire now crumbles down in pieces."


translate English day11_cr_76b2fe88_9:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_cr_8c4ae690:


    "\n I've misunderstood.{w} I thought I'd deceived her, that I'd been able to win her heart somehow.{w} That I could answer her expectations.{w} That we truly were lovers..."


translate English day11_cr_43498db5:


    "I was under the illusion that everything was going fine.{w} But in reality, nothing was fine, and everything was a mess."


translate English day11_cr_9e9254b3:


    "Very soon, I hear a woman's scream, then a man's.{w} People gather at this emergency stairwell, which once belonged only to us."


translate English day11_cr_d9b16e60:


    et "Having seen the skirt and hair ornaments, I hear Claire's name spoken here and there.{w} Her death--and my sin--become rumor so easily and quickly as to make all the time we spent together meaningless."


