translate English cr_end_1_e951837e:


    nar "A moment later, the unbearable terror wells up, almost like bile from my stomach." with sshake


translate English cr_end_1_f3dec803:


    nar "I suddenly realize that swallowing it is part of my reflection."


translate English cr_end_1_58a2c47e:


    nar "Until now, all I've been doing is wailing and wallowing in regret--I haven't reflected at all."


translate English cr_end_1_c158caa9:


    nar "But now, I can accept everything.{w} Claire died right before my eyes."


translate English cr_end_1_81d150b9:


